992
00:33:24,539 --> 00:33:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] To je moje dete, to je moje blagod.

993
00:33:27,539 --> 00:33:29,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam imao tih situacija.

994
00:33:29,180 --> 00:33:30,640
[SPEAKER_01] Neću govoriti mena, ali pazite,

995
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:33,299
[SPEAKER_01] imao sam mali, jedan, devet godina,

996
00:33:33,299 --> 00:33:34,500
[SPEAKER_01] imamo NTC kampove.

997
00:33:34,500 --> 00:33:36,240
[SPEAKER_01] Imamo, znači, Srbija, Hrvatska,

998
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:37,980
[SPEAKER_01] sad smo imali u Sloveniji, Crnogori.

999
00:33:37,980 --> 00:33:41,099
[SPEAKER_01] I taj mali dolazi, nisam ja znao

1000
00:33:41,099 --> 00:33:42,220
[SPEAKER_01] da on ima neki problem.

1001
00:33:42,220 --> 00:33:44,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ali vidim da se čudno ponaša.

1002
00:33:44,099 --> 00:33:47,500
[SPEAKER_01] Odjednom, on se trese

1003
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] i kreće da vrišti.

1004
00:33:48,619 --> 00:33:52,279
[SPEAKER_01] I brzo, šta je bilo, ništa.

1005
00:33:52,279 --> 00:33:56,500
[SPEAKER_01] Onda nije prošlo dugo,

1006
00:33:56,500 --> 00:33:58,180
[SPEAKER_01] dva sata, krene da vrišti

1007
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,140
[SPEAKER_01] i uzme do sebe,

1008
00:33:59,140 --> 00:34:00,819
[SPEAKER_01] devočicu čupe za kosu.

1009
00:34:00,819 --> 00:34:02,279
[SPEAKER_01] I brzo do njega, šta je to?

1010
00:34:02,279 --> 00:34:02,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ništa.

1011
00:34:02,920 --> 00:34:07,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ali on je agresivan prema slabio,

1012
00:34:07,099 --> 00:34:08,260
[SPEAKER_01] je djece ne prema jače.

1013
00:34:08,260 --> 00:34:09,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, on se kontroliše.

1014
00:34:09,400 --> 00:34:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, da ima neki implus,

1015
00:34:10,539 --> 00:34:12,199
[SPEAKER_01] bez koji mora negde da potroši.

1016
00:34:12,199 --> 00:34:14,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mu kažem,

1017
00:34:14,860 --> 00:34:16,320
[SPEAKER_01] slušaj,

1018
00:34:16,320 --> 00:34:17,440
[SPEAKER_01] ja budem malo strok

1019
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] na tom kampu.

1020
00:34:18,539 --> 00:34:19,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može baš sva

1021
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:21,340
[SPEAKER_01] deca da rade šta hoće.

1022
00:34:21,340 --> 00:34:22,880
[SPEAKER_01] U sve ne može niko da radi šta hoće.

1023
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:23,719
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, vidi,

1024
00:34:23,719 --> 00:34:25,920
[SPEAKER_01] ako se ovako budeš ponašao,

1025
00:34:25,920 --> 00:34:29,880
[SPEAKER_01] vraćamo te kući prvim autobusom.

1026
00:34:29,880 --> 00:34:33,719
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, nemojte, molim vas,

1027
00:34:33,719 --> 00:34:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] ubit će me mamu od batina.

1028
00:34:37,159 --> 00:34:38,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sad, svako pomisli,

1029
00:34:38,900 --> 00:34:40,719
[SPEAKER_01] možda će ga mamu ubiti od batina.

1030
00:34:40,719 --> 00:34:43,179
[SPEAKER_01] A redko ko pomisli,

1031
00:34:43,179 --> 00:34:44,780
[SPEAKER_01] možda manipuliše i sa mnom.

1032
00:34:44,780 --> 00:34:46,699
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, dobro,

1033
00:34:46,699 --> 00:34:48,980
[SPEAKER_01] neću te vratiti kući.

1034
00:34:48,980 --> 00:34:51,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako se ovako budeš ponašao,

1035
00:34:51,820 --> 00:34:53,599
[SPEAKER_01] ovo ti je žuti karton.

1036
00:34:53,599 --> 00:34:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] To će ti biti srveni,

1037
00:34:56,119 --> 00:34:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] ideš kući.

1038
00:34:56,860 --> 00:34:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] Nemora autobus,

1039
00:34:58,260 --> 00:34:59,400
[SPEAKER_01] evo ja ću da te vozim.

1040
00:34:59,400 --> 00:35:01,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ili ću svati mamu da dođe po tebe.

1041
00:35:01,199 --> 00:35:03,360
[SPEAKER_01] Nemojte, ali onda se kontroliši.

1042
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:06,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ako ti dođe to nešto,

1043
00:35:06,320 --> 00:35:07,400
[SPEAKER_01] vidim ja taj neki impuls,

1044
00:35:07,400 --> 00:35:08,880
[SPEAKER_01] idi trči u svoju sobu,

1045
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:09,920
[SPEAKER_01] pa tamo vrišti.

1046
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:12,840
[SPEAKER_01] I već popodne.

1047
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:14,900
[SPEAKER_01] Bili smo u kuhinju,

1048
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:16,500
[SPEAKER_01] čekali smo jer neko voće da uzmu,

1049
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:18,460
[SPEAKER_01] vidim ja njegom kreće da se namješta

1050
00:35:18,460 --> 00:35:20,880
[SPEAKER_01] i sprint u sobu.

1051
00:35:20,880 --> 00:35:22,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ja za njim.

1052
00:35:22,019 --> 00:35:24,280
[SPEAKER_01] On ulazi u sobu,

1053
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,159
[SPEAKER_01] kreće da vrišti.

1054
00:35:25,159 --> 00:35:27,219
[SPEAKER_01] Vrata sočkinota, gledam.

1055
00:35:27,219 --> 00:35:30,820
[SPEAKER_01] On vrišti, otvara plakar,

1056
00:35:30,820 --> 00:35:31,699
[SPEAKER_01] uzima knjigu

1057
00:35:31,699 --> 00:35:33,420
[SPEAKER_01] i kreće da liste knjigu

1058
00:35:33,420 --> 00:35:34,099
[SPEAKER_01] i smiri se.

1059
00:35:34,099 --> 00:35:35,239
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, kako je to knjiga,

1060
00:35:35,239 --> 00:35:36,099
[SPEAKER_01] čarobna knjiga,

1061
00:35:36,099 --> 00:35:38,000
[SPEAKER_01] kad ga ona smirila.

1062
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ulazim u sobu se,

1063
00:35:39,699 --> 00:35:40,400
[SPEAKER_01] dobro jesam.

1064
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] Šta to čitaš?

1065
00:35:41,519 --> 00:35:45,559
[SPEAKER_01] To su slike

1066
00:35:45,559 --> 00:35:47,039
[SPEAKER_01] iz neke videoigrice.

1067
00:35:47,039 --> 00:35:49,199
[SPEAKER_01] On gleda slike

1068
00:35:49,199 --> 00:35:49,760
[SPEAKER_01] iz videoigrice

1069
00:35:49,760 --> 00:35:50,480
[SPEAKER_01] i smirio se.

1070
00:35:52,519 --> 00:35:52,760
[SPEAKER_01] dobro.

1071
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:53,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sad pitam,

1072
00:35:53,760 --> 00:35:55,739
[SPEAKER_01] te od njegove sobe su prijatelji

1073
00:35:55,739 --> 00:35:56,980
[SPEAKER_01] iz istog dela grada su.

1074
00:35:56,980 --> 00:35:59,059
[SPEAKER_01] Pitam, recite mi,

1075
00:35:59,059 --> 00:36:00,199
[SPEAKER_01] kako se on ponašao?

1076
00:36:00,199 --> 00:36:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kaže isto.

1077
00:36:01,760 --> 00:36:02,380
[SPEAKER_01] A što radice?

1078
00:36:02,380 --> 00:36:03,519
[SPEAKER_01] Sada vidim tu videoigricu

1079
00:36:03,519 --> 00:36:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] da ima knjigu.

1080
00:36:04,079 --> 00:36:05,260
[SPEAKER_01] A pa on igra videoigrice

1081
00:36:05,260 --> 00:36:05,719
[SPEAKER_01] po sedem,

1082
00:36:05,719 --> 00:36:06,219
[SPEAKER_01] osam sati,

1083
00:36:06,219 --> 00:36:07,260
[SPEAKER_01] on se ne igra sa nama.

1084
00:36:07,260 --> 00:36:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] To znači on igra sedem,

1085
00:36:09,380 --> 00:36:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] osam sati videoigricu

1086
00:36:10,539 --> 00:36:11,280
[SPEAKER_01] kad ide u školu,

1087
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] kad spava.

1088
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,159
[SPEAKER_01] I ja svatim,

1089
00:36:13,159 --> 00:36:13,639
[SPEAKER_01] pa to je

1090
00:36:13,639 --> 00:36:15,820
[SPEAKER_01] ovisnost ili zavisnost

1091
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:16,599
[SPEAKER_01] od videoigrice.

1092
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:18,420
[SPEAKER_01] agresivno ponašanje.

1093
00:36:18,420 --> 00:36:20,840
[SPEAKER_01] Nemo osjećaj za druge.

1094
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da dobiju to što želi.

1095
00:36:22,699 --> 00:36:24,780
[SPEAKER_01] I malo sam tu kontrolisao.

1096
00:36:24,780 --> 00:36:27,860
[SPEAKER_01] I pišem posle kampu,

1097
00:36:27,860 --> 00:36:28,739
[SPEAKER_01] obično roditeljima,

1098
00:36:28,739 --> 00:36:29,719
[SPEAKER_01] pošaljemo pismo.

1099
00:36:29,719 --> 00:36:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] Da se deto uklopilo,

1100
00:36:32,880 --> 00:36:33,900
[SPEAKER_01] da se nije uklopilo,

1101
00:36:33,900 --> 00:36:35,400
[SPEAKER_01] da smo videli da je tu dobro,

1102
00:36:35,400 --> 00:36:36,159
[SPEAKER_01] da ovde nije dobro

1103
00:36:36,159 --> 00:36:37,300
[SPEAKER_01] da malo to pojačuju.

1104
00:36:37,300 --> 00:36:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pišem pismo da smo to primetili,

1105
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:39,940
[SPEAKER_01] ali ja lepo napišem

1106
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:41,599
[SPEAKER_01] da bi dobro bilo

1107
00:36:41,599 --> 00:36:42,619
[SPEAKER_01] da upišo na sport.

1108
00:36:42,619 --> 00:36:45,019
[SPEAKER_01] Da pokazuje znake

1109
00:36:45,019 --> 00:36:46,300
[SPEAKER_01] zavisnosti od videoigrice.

1110
00:36:47,300 --> 00:36:48,440
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je mama odgovorila?

1111
00:36:48,440 --> 00:36:49,039
[SPEAKER_01] Šta mislite?

1112
00:36:49,039 --> 00:36:53,159
[SPEAKER_01] Šta mislite?

1113
00:36:53,159 --> 00:36:53,840
[SPEAKER_01] Evo sad ste vi

1114
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:55,300
[SPEAKER_01] ranko i postavite pismo

1115
00:36:55,300 --> 00:36:55,860
[SPEAKER_01] jednoj ženi

1116
00:36:55,860 --> 00:36:57,019
[SPEAKER_01] da joj pomognete za sina.

1117
00:36:57,019 --> 00:36:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] I šta je mama odgovorila?

1118
00:36:58,340 --> 00:36:59,679
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ovo pitanje.

1119
00:36:59,679 --> 00:37:00,460
[SPEAKER_01] Svi ko nas gledaju,

1120
00:37:00,460 --> 00:37:01,519
[SPEAKER_01] evo i vi probajte

1121
00:37:01,519 --> 00:37:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] da govorite

1122
00:37:02,039 --> 00:37:02,840
[SPEAKER_01] šta je ta žena

1123
00:37:02,840 --> 00:37:03,699
[SPEAKER_01] meni napisala.

1124
00:37:03,699 --> 00:37:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] A lepo sam pismo napisao

1125
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,900
[SPEAKER_01] da malo smanje vidi

1126
00:37:06,900 --> 00:37:08,360
[SPEAKER_01] ingrice da gupiše na sport.

1127
00:37:08,360 --> 00:37:10,699
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je ona odgovorila?

1128
00:37:10,699 --> 00:37:11,639
[SPEAKER_01] Napala vas?

1129
00:37:11,639 --> 00:37:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ili je?

1130
00:37:13,139 --> 00:37:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] Kako?

1131
00:37:14,659 --> 00:37:16,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kako me napala?

1132
00:37:16,599 --> 00:37:17,440
[SPEAKER_01] Jeste na Falome.

1133
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:21,139
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kritizirali ste nju zapravo?

1134
00:37:21,139 --> 00:37:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] Napisale.

1135
00:37:22,739 --> 00:37:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] Moj sin,

1136
00:37:24,659 --> 00:37:26,059
[SPEAKER_01] moje zlato,

1137
00:37:26,059 --> 00:37:27,280
[SPEAKER_01] moje blago.

1138
00:37:27,280 --> 00:37:29,039
[SPEAKER_01] Pa njega svi vole,

1139
00:37:29,039 --> 00:37:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] svi govore

1140
00:37:29,940 --> 00:37:30,860
[SPEAKER_01] kako je to dobro,

1141
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:31,320
[SPEAKER_01] dete,

1142
00:37:31,320 --> 00:37:32,820
[SPEAKER_01] ja sa vama vero,

1143
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] ali vi ste jedini

1144
00:37:33,800 --> 00:37:34,320
[SPEAKER_01] napisali

1145
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:35,300
[SPEAKER_01] da ona ima neki problem.

1146
00:37:35,300 --> 00:37:36,460
[SPEAKER_01] Kako to možete?

1147
00:37:36,460 --> 00:37:37,360
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

1148
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:38,420
[SPEAKER_01] drvlje, kamenje.

1149
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] I onda napišem drugo pismo.

1150
00:37:41,119 --> 00:37:42,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kako god hoćete.

1151
00:37:42,519 --> 00:37:45,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ali deco ko već pokazuju

1152
00:37:45,420 --> 00:37:45,900
[SPEAKER_01] zavisnost,

1153
00:37:45,900 --> 00:37:47,400
[SPEAKER_01] ovisnost u devetoj,

1154
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:48,300
[SPEAKER_01] desetoj godini,

1155
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:50,539
[SPEAKER_01] već po istraživanjima

1156
00:37:50,539 --> 00:37:51,440
[SPEAKER_01] će tražiti

1157
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:52,360
[SPEAKER_01] novu stimulaciju,

1158
00:37:52,360 --> 00:37:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] gde?

1159
00:37:52,539 --> 00:37:54,320
[SPEAKER_01] Pa možda u narkoticima sutra.

1160
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:56,460
[SPEAKER_01] Izgubit ćemo decu.

1161
00:37:57,320 --> 00:37:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] Roditelji često ne prihvati

1162
00:37:58,739 --> 00:37:59,300
[SPEAKER_01] o kritiku.

1163
00:37:59,300 --> 00:38:00,599
[SPEAKER_01] I zato kažem,

1164
00:38:00,599 --> 00:38:02,199
[SPEAKER_01] roditelji je odgovoran

1165
00:38:02,199 --> 00:38:03,039
[SPEAKER_01] za odgoj.

1166
00:38:03,039 --> 00:38:04,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dete je krenulo u školu.

1167
00:38:04,699 --> 00:38:05,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ko prvi vidi

1168
00:38:05,820 --> 00:38:06,579
[SPEAKER_01] da nešto ne u redu

1169
00:38:06,579 --> 00:38:07,280
[SPEAKER_01] sa decetom

1170
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] među 25 ili 30 učenika?

1171
00:38:09,500 --> 00:38:10,480
[SPEAKER_01] Učiteljica.

1172
00:38:10,480 --> 00:38:12,739
[SPEAKER_01] I to treba svaki roditelj

1173
00:38:12,739 --> 00:38:13,139
[SPEAKER_01] da zna.

1174
00:38:13,139 --> 00:38:14,780
[SPEAKER_01] Učiteljica je poslednja

1175
00:38:14,780 --> 00:38:15,780
[SPEAKER_01] ona linija

1176
00:38:15,780 --> 00:38:16,659
[SPEAKER_01] koja može

1177
00:38:16,659 --> 00:38:17,780
[SPEAKER_01] da urode neku reakciju

1178
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:18,739
[SPEAKER_01] da pomogne detetu.

1179
00:38:18,739 --> 00:38:21,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ako mi priječamo

1180
00:38:21,119 --> 00:38:23,099
[SPEAKER_01] da učiteljica nije dobra,

1181
00:38:23,099 --> 00:38:24,920
[SPEAKER_01] da ona ne znam svoj posao,

1182
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:26,239
[SPEAKER_01] da ko zna

1183
00:38:26,239 --> 00:38:27,159
[SPEAKER_01] kakva je

1184
00:38:27,159 --> 00:38:28,320
[SPEAKER_01] i roditelji

1185
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,460
[SPEAKER_01] svašta priča učiteljima.

1186
00:38:29,460 --> 00:38:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] Učenik tog sekunda

1187
00:38:31,940 --> 00:38:33,159
[SPEAKER_01] gubi respekt.

1188
00:38:33,159 --> 00:38:35,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ko će njemu pomoći?

1189
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] Pa niko.

1190
00:38:37,480 --> 00:38:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] Pa li imate roditelji,

1191
00:38:38,920 --> 00:38:39,780
[SPEAKER_01] teri učitelje

1192
00:38:39,780 --> 00:38:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] da poklonu ocenu?

1193
00:38:41,940 --> 00:38:44,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ne sa četvorke na peticu,

1194
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,440
[SPEAKER_01] sa trojke na peticu.

1195
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:48,199
[SPEAKER_01] Kao da će to nešto pomoći.

1196
00:38:48,199 --> 00:38:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] Dupišu, ne znam šta.

1197
00:38:49,539 --> 00:38:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je se desilo

1198
00:38:50,579 --> 00:38:51,739
[SPEAKER_01] od Crne Gori pre pet godina,

1199
00:38:51,739 --> 00:38:53,239
[SPEAKER_01] često pokažem na predavanju.

1200
00:38:53,239 --> 00:38:55,400
[SPEAKER_01] Od 102 kandidata

1201
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:56,780
[SPEAKER_01] za upis na medicinske fakulte,

1202
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:59,699
[SPEAKER_01] u te 90 nije položilo

1203
00:38:59,699 --> 00:39:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] prijemni ispit.

1204
00:39:00,420 --> 00:39:02,280
