[SPEAKER_01] ako i stignu za dvjeti godine

1312
00:41:14,559 --> 00:41:15,460
[SPEAKER_01] da malo podignu

1313
00:41:15,460 --> 00:41:16,440
[SPEAKER_01] na nekadašnji nivo,

1314
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:18,340
