1331
00:41:47,900 --> 00:41:49,280
[SPEAKER_01] da pišu, da čitaju,

1332
00:41:49,380 --> 00:41:49,980
[SPEAKER_01] da slušaju,

1333
00:41:49,980 --> 00:41:50,920
[SPEAKER_01] da pamte.

1334
00:41:50,920 --> 00:41:52,420
