1341
00:42:05,639 --> 00:42:07,260
[SPEAKER_01] traže se odlaganje godinu dana.

1342
00:42:07,260 --> 00:42:10,599
[SPEAKER_01] A još 20% treba dodatno pomoć

1343
00:42:10,599 --> 00:42:13,519
[SPEAKER_01] psihologa, pedagoga, defektologa.

1344
00:42:13,519 --> 00:42:14,679
[SPEAKER_01] pa šta je ovo?

1345
00:42:14,679 --> 00:42:16,920
[SPEAKER_01] Iako ne budemo ništa promenili,

1346
