[SPEAKER_01] I tu su nam roditelji odgovorni,

1354
00:42:32,260 --> 00:42:33,099
[SPEAKER_01] nisu krivi,

1355
00:42:33,099 --> 00:42:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] a sistem vrtiće moraju da poprave.

1356
00:42:35,539 --> 00:42:37,699
[SPEAKER_01] I tu ima šest nekih faktora

1357
00:42:37,699 --> 00:42:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] zašto su deca sve slabije.

1358
00:42:39,980 --> 00:42:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] Znači mi moramo prvo da gledamo

1359
00:42:41,539 --> 00:42:43,059
[SPEAKER_01] razvoju mozga do šeste godine.

1360
00:42:43,059 --> 00:42:44,780
