1368
00:42:57,699 --> 00:42:59,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ovako kako je sad.

1369
00:42:59,039 --> 00:43:00,059
[SPEAKER_01] Pitanje je,

1370
00:43:00,059 --> 00:43:02,139
[SPEAKER_01] jel sad za medicinu u Podgorici,

1371
00:43:02,139 --> 00:43:03,940
[SPEAKER_01] pa ko će nas sutra da leči?

1372
00:43:03,940 --> 00:43:06,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ko će da pravi mostove, tunele?

1373
00:43:06,619 --> 00:43:07,659
[SPEAKER_01] Kinezi?

1374
00:43:07,659 --> 00:43:09,199
[SPEAKER_01] Gde smo mi?

1375
00:43:09,199 --> 00:43:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, jako je ozbiljno sad ovo,

1376
00:43:12,420 --> 00:43:13,940
[SPEAKER_01] jer vreme za reforme

1377
