1392
00:43:39,880 --> 00:43:40,559
[SPEAKER_01] nego ranije.

1393
00:43:41,920 --> 00:43:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] A to znači samo jedno.

1394
00:43:43,420 --> 00:43:46,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je država nekad nastajala

1395
00:43:46,199 --> 00:43:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] i nestajala za 500 godina,

1396
00:43:48,380 --> 00:43:50,780
[SPEAKER_01] to će danas biti za 50.

1397
00:43:50,780 --> 00:43:54,239
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ako imamo 20, 30 generacija

1398
00:43:54,239 --> 00:43:57,360
[SPEAKER_01] slabije sposobne dece ili nesposobne dece?

1399
00:43:58,000 --> 00:43:59,519
[SPEAKER_01] Pa druge narodi nas prekrivaju.

1400
00:43:59,519 --> 00:44:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] To znači,

1401
00:44:00,619 --> 00:44:03,460
[SPEAKER_01] obrazovanje je stup društva.

1402
00:44:03,460 --> 00:44:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek je bilo.

1403
00:44:04,280 --> 00:44:06,139
[SPEAKER_01] A će sad da se vidi jako brzo.

1404
00:44:06,139 --> 00:44:08,800
[SPEAKER_01] Nema tu vremena 10-20 godina za reforme.

1405
00:44:08,800 --> 00:44:10,559
[SPEAKER_01] I ono što predem,

1406
00:44:10,559 --> 00:44:11,679
