[SPEAKER_01] sad idem Kanada, Amerike,

1408
00:44:12,880 --> 00:44:14,239
[SPEAKER_01] o treći put za godinu dana,

1409
00:44:14,239 --> 00:44:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] reforme ne mogu više

1410
00:44:16,099 --> 00:44:18,219
[SPEAKER_01] ili možda mogu na nevou države

1411
00:44:18,219 --> 00:44:19,579
[SPEAKER_01] okvirna reforma

1412
00:44:19,579 --> 00:44:21,559
[SPEAKER_01] i u hodu da se rešava.

1413
00:44:21,559 --> 00:44:24,159
[SPEAKER_01] Da čak mislim da će svaki grad,

1414
00:44:24,159 --> 00:44:26,119
[SPEAKER_01] svaka regija morati da brine za sebe.

1415
00:44:26,119 --> 00:44:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] To da čekamo rješenje,

1416
00:44:28,000 --> 00:44:28,820
[SPEAKER_01] državni nivo,

1417
00:44:28,820 --> 00:44:30,300
[SPEAKER_01] pet pilot projekata,

1418
00:44:30,300 --> 00:44:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] idemo 10 godina,

1419
00:44:31,420 --> 00:44:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] jesmo pogrešili jednu setnicu,

1420
00:44:33,519 --> 00:44:34,099
[SPEAKER_01] gotovi smo.

1421
00:44:34,099 --> 00:44:36,679
[SPEAKER_01] Či morat će u hodu da se radi reforma.

1422
00:44:36,679 --> 00:44:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] Eto, to predem na fakultetu,

1423
00:44:39,039 --> 00:44:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] znači neuroznanost,

1424
00:44:40,880 --> 00:44:42,500
[SPEAKER_01] uzgoj in izobraževanju,

1425
00:44:42,500 --> 00:44:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] odgoj i obrazovanju,

1426
00:44:43,380 --> 00:44:46,079
[SPEAKER_01] moramo da učimo buduće naše pedagoge,

1427
00:44:46,079 --> 00:44:47,599
[SPEAKER_01] psihologe, učitelje,

1428
00:44:48,000 --> 00:44:51,139
[SPEAKER_01] kako da oni u hodu rešavaju probleme.

1429
00:44:51,139 --> 00:44:55,280
[SPEAKER_02] Koja je onda zapravo fundamentalna razlika

1430
00:44:55,280 --> 00:44:56,119
[SPEAKER_02] između generacije?

1431
00:44:56,119 --> 00:44:59,260
[SPEAKER_02] Recimo, u doba kaste vi bili djete

1432
00:44:59,260 --> 00:45:01,719
[SPEAKER_02] ili danas recimo kad je možnje?

1433
00:45:01,719 --> 00:45:05,019
[SPEAKER_02] A što je fundamentalna razlika uopće?

1434
00:45:05,019 --> 00:45:06,579
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ću reći formiranje mozga,

1435
00:45:06,579 --> 00:45:08,119
[SPEAKER_01] znači drugače ponašanje,

1436
00:45:08,119 --> 00:45:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] drugače vrednosti života,

1437
00:45:10,579 --> 00:45:12,940
[SPEAKER_01] znači nepotpuno drugače

1438
00:45:12,940 --> 00:45:14,760
[SPEAKER_01] percepiraju društvo

1439
00:45:14,760 --> 00:45:19,039
[SPEAKER_01] i recimo neke stvari nego mi.

1440
00:45:19,039 --> 00:45:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1441
00:45:20,239 --> 00:45:23,260
[SPEAKER_01] Jel ako je okruženje važno 100%,

1442
00:45:23,260 --> 00:45:24,199
[SPEAKER_01] a reku sam da je,

1443
00:45:24,199 --> 00:45:25,880
[SPEAKER_01] znači genetika je važna,

1444
00:45:25,880 --> 00:45:26,940
[SPEAKER_01] 100% to je potencijal.

1445
00:45:26,940 --> 00:45:29,159
[SPEAKER_01] A razum mozga zavisa od okruženja,

1446
00:45:29,159 --> 00:45:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] kad?

1447
00:45:29,420 --> 00:45:30,840
[SPEAKER_01] Pa tog se forivera mozak,

1448
00:45:30,840 --> 00:45:31,900
[SPEAKER_01] prve 3-4 godine.

1449
00:45:31,900 --> 00:45:33,639
[SPEAKER_01] Znači okruženje je ključno,

1450
00:45:33,639 --> 00:45:35,199
[SPEAKER_01] pa čak je do 5-7.

1451
00:45:35,199 --> 00:45:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] I sad, samo da bih to objasnio,

1452
00:45:39,260 --> 00:45:42,239
[SPEAKER_01] zašto je za mozak genetika 100% okruženje 100%,

1453
00:45:42,239 --> 00:45:43,440
[SPEAKER_01] a za boju očiju,

1454
00:45:43,440 --> 00:45:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] genetika je 100% okruženje nula.

1455
00:45:46,539 --> 00:45:49,079
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ljudi budu zbunjeni,

1456
00:45:49,079 --> 00:45:52,099
[SPEAKER_01] kako mislite za mozak 100% jedno 100% drugo,

1457
00:45:52,099 --> 00:45:53,659
[SPEAKER_01] a za boju očiju,

1458
00:45:53,659 --> 00:45:55,340
[SPEAKER_01] pa genetika je 100%,

1459
00:45:55,340 --> 00:45:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] i onda objasnim za mozak.

1460
00:45:58,019 --> 00:45:59,980
[SPEAKER_01] Mi kad se rodimo,

1461
00:45:59,980 --> 00:46:01,400
[SPEAKER_01] mozak nije završao razvoj,

1462
00:46:01,400 --> 00:46:02,300
[SPEAKER_01] to je siva masa,

1463
00:46:02,300 --> 00:46:03,940
[SPEAKER_01] to nema nernih puteva.

1464
00:46:03,940 --> 00:46:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] I te kad se rodimo,

1465
00:46:05,960 --> 00:46:07,179
[SPEAKER_01] kreću nerni putevi.

1466
00:46:07,179 --> 00:46:08,920
[SPEAKER_01] Pitanje je,

1467
00:46:08,920 --> 00:46:11,820
[SPEAKER_01] zašto naš mozak nije završao razvoj

1468
00:46:11,820 --> 00:46:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] u trudnoći?

1469
00:46:12,500 --> 00:46:14,340
[SPEAKER_01] Rećemo, druga živa bića.

1470
00:46:14,340 --> 00:46:16,739
[SPEAKER_01] Za par sati, za par dana

1471
00:46:16,739 --> 00:46:18,679
[SPEAKER_01] su operativna mala žirafa.

1472
00:46:18,679 --> 00:46:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ona mora da stane na noge

1473
00:46:20,940 --> 00:46:23,019
[SPEAKER_01] jako brzo da krene da trče za mamom.

1474
00:46:23,019 --> 00:46:23,760
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1475
00:46:24,460 --> 00:46:25,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa pošće lavovi.

1476
00:46:25,539 --> 00:46:28,260
[SPEAKER_01] A mi,

1477
00:46:28,260 --> 00:46:30,139
[SPEAKER_01] po profesoru Lichtmanu,

1478
00:46:30,139 --> 00:46:30,940
[SPEAKER_01] sa Harvarda,

1479
00:46:30,940 --> 00:46:32,860
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo fetusi do 13. godine.

1480
00:46:32,860 --> 00:46:35,280
[SPEAKER_01] Kako nismo si tako tvrdni,

1481
00:46:35,280 --> 00:46:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] a čovjek će možda dobiti

1482
00:46:36,380 --> 00:46:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] i Nobelovu nagradu,

1483
00:46:37,500 --> 00:46:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] kako fetusi do 13. godine?

1484
00:46:39,260 --> 00:46:41,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pa zato što nama treba

1485
00:46:41,239 --> 00:46:42,739
[SPEAKER_01] tuđaj pomoć da bi preživjeli.

1486
00:46:42,739 --> 00:46:45,139
[SPEAKER_01] I u stvari,

1487
00:46:45,139 --> 00:46:48,159
[SPEAKER_01] tu je odgovor na sve to što sad pričam.

1488
00:46:48,159 --> 00:46:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] Pa naš mozak je jako velik.

1489
00:46:50,119 --> 00:46:53,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može da završi razvoj u trudnoći.

1490
00:46:53,579 --> 00:46:54,219
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

1491
00:46:54,219 --> 00:46:56,519
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ako bi mozg bio malo veći,

1492
00:46:56,519 --> 00:46:59,460
[SPEAKER_01] onda bi glava bila pa malo veća

1493
00:46:59,460 --> 00:47:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] i ne bi mogli da se rodimo.

1494
00:47:01,000 --> 00:47:03,480
[SPEAKER_01] To znači mi ljudi se rađimo kad

1495
00:47:03,480 --> 00:47:05,280
[SPEAKER_01] u poslednjem momentu

1496
00:47:05,280 --> 00:47:06,940
[SPEAKER_01] doga glava može da prođe

1497
00:47:06,940 --> 00:47:08,119
[SPEAKER_01] kroz porođeni kanal.

1498
00:47:08,820 --> 00:47:10,099
[SPEAKER_01] Čak imamo dve fontanela

1499
00:47:10,099 --> 00:47:11,400
[SPEAKER_01] da se ta glava stisne.

1500
00:47:11,400 --> 00:47:13,940
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kreće razvoj mozga.

1501
00:47:13,940 --> 00:47:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] Od čega zavisi?

1502
00:47:15,480 --> 00:47:16,579
[SPEAKER_01] Od okruženja.

1503
00:47:16,579 --> 00:47:18,239
[SPEAKER_01] I tada kreće formiranje

1504
00:47:18,239 --> 00:47:20,019
[SPEAKER_01] nernih puteva i sinapsi.

1505
00:47:20,019 --> 00:47:21,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa čak profesorica

1506
00:47:21,539 --> 00:47:23,099
[SPEAKER_01] Marian Daymond iz Kalifornije

1507
00:47:23,099 --> 00:47:23,599
[SPEAKER_01] uradila,

1508
00:47:23,599 --> 00:47:25,219
[SPEAKER_01] sad već čujan eksperiment,

1509
00:47:25,219 --> 00:47:27,420
[SPEAKER_01] uzela je dve grupe

1510
00:47:27,420 --> 00:47:28,599
[SPEAKER_01] genetski potpuno iste.

1511
00:47:29,440 --> 00:47:32,199
[SPEAKER_01] Jedna grupa ima vodiju hranu,

1512
00:47:32,199 --> 00:47:33,440
[SPEAKER_01] a druga grupa

1513
00:47:33,440 --> 00:47:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] nema vodiju hranu,

1514
00:47:35,539 --> 00:47:36,420
[SPEAKER_01] ima laverinte.

1515
00:47:36,420 --> 00:47:38,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ona druga grupa mora da misli

1516
00:47:38,559 --> 00:47:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] gde da skrene,

1517
00:47:40,019 --> 00:47:40,760
[SPEAKER_01] gde da stane,

1518
00:47:40,760 --> 00:47:41,780
[SPEAKER_01] gde da se provuče

1519
00:47:41,780 --> 00:47:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] da bi došle do vode hrane.

1520
00:47:42,980 --> 00:47:45,639
[SPEAKER_01] Kad su za, ne znam,

1521
00:47:45,639 --> 00:47:47,739
[SPEAKER_01] 15 dana završili eksperiment,

1522
00:47:47,739 --> 00:47:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] grupa B je bila 50% inteligentnija.

1523
00:47:52,139 --> 00:47:53,400
[SPEAKER_01] A genetski su isti.

1524
00:47:53,400 --> 00:47:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] Šta dalje vidjeli ispod mikroskopa?

1525
00:47:55,539 --> 00:47:58,820
[SPEAKER_01] Grupa B imala veći broj sinapsi

1526
00:47:58,820 --> 00:47:59,760
[SPEAKER_01] od grupe A.

1527
00:47:59,760 --> 00:48:02,260
[SPEAKER_01] Znači sad imamo dokaz

1528
00:48:02,260 --> 00:48:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] da od tih sinapse,

1529
00:48:03,960 --> 00:48:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] od tih veza zavisi inteligencija.

1530
00:48:05,940 --> 00:48:07,219
[SPEAKER_01] I sad da poslijemo,

1531
00:48:07,219 --> 00:48:08,400
[SPEAKER_01] šta su onda neuroni?

1532
00:48:08,400 --> 00:48:09,659
[SPEAKER_01] Evo mi ljudi dobijemo

1533
00:48:09,659 --> 00:48:10,960
[SPEAKER_01] 100 milijarde neurona

1534
00:48:10,960 --> 00:48:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] od mami i tate.

1535
00:48:12,079 --> 00:48:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] To je genetika.

1536
00:48:13,039 --> 00:48:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] A kako će se povezati?

1537
00:48:15,480 --> 00:48:17,260
[SPEAKER_01] To su sinapse,

1538
00:48:17,260 --> 00:48:19,059
[SPEAKER_01] to je okruženje.

1539
00:48:19,059 --> 00:48:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] I sad razumijemo,

1540
00:48:20,239 --> 00:48:21,699
[SPEAKER_01] genetika 100% okruženje,

1541
00:48:21,699 --> 00:48:22,639
[SPEAKER_01] skoro 100%,

1542
00:48:22,639 --> 00:48:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] jer neke sinapse,

1543
00:48:24,500 --> 00:48:25,119
[SPEAKER_01] kad se rodimo,

1544
00:48:25,119 --> 00:48:26,599
[SPEAKER_01] ostano većina se resorbuje.

1545
00:48:26,599 --> 00:48:28,579
[SPEAKER_01] To znači okruženje,

1546
00:48:28,699 --> 00:48:31,400
[SPEAKER_01] menja strukturu našeg mozga.

1547
00:48:31,400 --> 00:48:33,199
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ne može biti isto

1548
00:48:33,199 --> 00:48:34,400
[SPEAKER_01] neko ko se rodio

1549
00:48:34,400 --> 00:48:36,019
[SPEAKER_01] pre 50 i više godina,

1550
00:48:36,019 --> 00:48:37,699
[SPEAKER_01] jer su deca trčala

1551
00:48:37,699 --> 00:48:39,599
[SPEAKER_01] nevno po 10-20 kilometara.

1552
00:48:39,599 --> 00:48:41,199
[SPEAKER_01] Kretenje je jako važno.

1553
00:48:41,199 --> 00:48:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] A danas,

1554
00:48:42,699 --> 00:48:44,460
[SPEAKER_01] nema toliko kretenja.

1555
00:48:44,460 --> 00:48:45,699
[SPEAKER_01] Evo kolica do druge,

1556
00:48:45,699 --> 00:48:46,400
[SPEAKER_01] treće godine.

1557
00:48:47,860 --> 00:48:52,860
[SPEAKER_01] pa pitajte neke starije ljudi od 70-80 godina,

1558
00:48:52,860 --> 00:48:55,159
[SPEAKER_01] da li še imali kolice za svoje dete?

1559
00:48:55,159 --> 00:48:57,199
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je imao svaka peta mama kolica,

1560
00:48:57,199 --> 00:48:58,519
[SPEAKER_01] ako je imala i godinu dana,

1561
00:48:58,519 --> 00:48:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] a danas,

1562
00:48:59,480 --> 00:49:02,039
[SPEAKER_01] kolice do 34. godine.

1563
00:49:02,039 --> 00:49:03,559
[SPEAKER_01] Nema kretenja.

1564
00:49:04,519 --> 00:49:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] onda ne damo dete da padne,

1565
00:49:06,480 --> 00:49:07,699
[SPEAKER_01] da se ne povredi.

1566
00:49:07,699 --> 00:49:09,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ne damo da se penje na drvo.

1567
00:49:09,960 --> 00:49:13,239
[SPEAKER_01] A mi smo se penjali po drveću,

1568
00:49:13,239 --> 00:49:14,480
[SPEAKER_01] niko nije ni gledao šta radimo.

1569
00:49:15,179 --> 00:49:16,519
[SPEAKER_01] sumo kažu dođite na ručak,

1570
00:49:16,519 --> 00:49:17,840
[SPEAKER_01] dođite na večeru.

1571
00:49:17,840 --> 00:49:20,420
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo se penjali po drveću,

1572
00:49:20,420 --> 00:49:20,940
[SPEAKER_01] skakali,

1573
00:49:20,940 --> 00:49:21,619
[SPEAKER_01] priskakali,

1574
00:49:21,619 --> 00:49:22,300
[SPEAKER_01] provlačili,

1575
00:49:22,300 --> 00:49:24,260
[SPEAKER_01] hodili po nekim i višnjacima.

1576
00:49:24,260 --> 00:49:25,880
[SPEAKER_01] Znači mi smo imali u tom kretenju

1577
00:49:25,880 --> 00:49:26,639
[SPEAKER_01] njako puno stvari

1578
00:49:26,639 --> 00:49:27,719
[SPEAKER_01] koje formiraju mozak.

1579
00:49:27,719 --> 00:49:29,360
[SPEAKER_01] A naše dete danas

1580
00:49:29,360 --> 00:49:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] ne sme da padne,

1581
00:49:31,960 --> 00:49:32,880
[SPEAKER_01] ne sme da skače,

1582
00:49:32,880 --> 00:49:33,739
[SPEAKER_01] ne sme na drveće,

1583
00:49:33,739 --> 00:49:34,639
[SPEAKER_01] ne sme ni izbrdo.

1584
00:49:34,639 --> 00:49:37,340
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da bi dete bilo sigurno,

1585
00:49:37,340 --> 00:49:38,840
[SPEAKER_01] kupimo TV,

1586
00:49:38,840 --> 00:49:39,820
[SPEAKER_01] usobjedimo TV

1587
00:49:39,820 --> 00:49:41,940
[SPEAKER_01] i odjednom oduzimamo kretenje,

1588
00:49:41,940 --> 00:49:42,820
[SPEAKER_01] istraživanje

1589
00:49:42,820 --> 00:49:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] i dolazi do promjenu radu mozga.

1590
00:49:45,400 --> 00:49:47,659
[SPEAKER_01] To znači da svaka,

1591
00:49:47,659 --> 00:49:49,360
[SPEAKER_01] sad već na deset godina,

1592
00:49:49,360 --> 00:49:50,480
[SPEAKER_01] kako se okruženje menja,

1593
00:49:50,480 --> 00:49:51,880
[SPEAKER_01] drugačije je ponačanje

1594
00:49:51,880 --> 00:49:53,099
[SPEAKER_01] svake nove generacije.

1595
00:49:53,099 --> 00:49:55,360
[SPEAKER_01] I sad da vidim na ove generacije,

1596
00:49:55,360 --> 00:49:56,780
[SPEAKER_01] mi kad smo radili pre deset godina,

1597
00:49:56,780 --> 00:49:58,260
[SPEAKER_01] da već tada su učitelji

1598
00:49:58,260 --> 00:49:59,019
[SPEAKER_01] govorili da su oni

1599
00:49:59,019 --> 00:49:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] kognitivno slabiji.

1600
00:49:59,960 --> 00:50:01,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pre deset godina.

1601
00:50:01,239 --> 00:50:03,239
[SPEAKER_01] Dolaze na fakultet,

1602
00:50:03,239 --> 00:50:04,360
[SPEAKER_01] nema predavno fakultetu.

1603
00:50:04,360 --> 00:50:05,920
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro su deca.

1604
00:50:05,920 --> 00:50:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] Imaju empatiju,

1605
00:50:08,099 --> 00:50:09,039
[SPEAKER_01] osjećaj za druge,

1606
00:50:09,039 --> 00:50:10,380
[SPEAKER_01] hoće da pomognu,

1607
00:50:10,380 --> 00:50:12,380
[SPEAKER_01] ali kognitivno jesu slabiji.

1608
00:50:13,820 --> 00:50:15,440
[SPEAKER_01] Nema tog rezonovanja visokog.

1609
00:50:15,440 --> 00:50:17,760
[SPEAKER_01] I sad je naravno pitanje

1610
00:50:17,760 --> 00:50:18,980
[SPEAKER_01] na celom društvu,

1611
00:50:18,980 --> 00:50:19,619
[SPEAKER_01] šta ćemo mi,

1612
00:50:19,619 --> 00:50:21,199
[SPEAKER_01] kompjuter su nas pobedili

1613
00:50:21,199 --> 00:50:22,760
[SPEAKER_01] po informacijama i kombinacijama.

1614
00:50:22,760 --> 00:50:25,179
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, učenje na pamet,

1615
00:50:25,179 --> 00:50:28,719
[SPEAKER_01] to je učenje za prošlost.

1616
00:50:30,219 --> 00:50:31,519
[SPEAKER_01] Mi moramo da učemo decu

1617
00:50:31,519 --> 00:50:32,900
[SPEAKER_01] na drugačiji način,

