2274
01:05:02,820 --> 01:05:05,079
[SPEAKER_01] Onda neko kaže,

2275
01:05:05,079 --> 01:05:08,679
[SPEAKER_01] pa možda je teša 40 kg.

2276
01:05:08,679 --> 01:05:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, odlično,

2277
01:05:09,840 --> 01:05:10,760
[SPEAKER_01] jako velika ptica,

2278
01:05:10,760 --> 01:05:11,880
[SPEAKER_01] ali ima 20 kg.

2279
01:05:11,880 --> 01:05:13,019
[SPEAKER_01] I oni onaka kao,

2280
01:05:13,019 --> 01:05:14,480
[SPEAKER_01] jao, kako su upravo možili.

2281
01:05:14,480 --> 01:05:15,619
[SPEAKER_01] Svi hoće pogoditi.

2282
01:05:15,619 --> 01:05:17,159
[SPEAKER_01] Da, i onda šta dobijemo

2283
01:05:17,159 --> 01:05:18,000
[SPEAKER_01] da je 40,

2284
01:05:18,000 --> 01:05:19,539
[SPEAKER_01] pošto puno leti.

2285
01:05:19,539 --> 01:05:21,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ako leti iznad Pacifika,

2286
01:05:21,139 --> 01:05:21,739
[SPEAKER_01] gde je spava?

2287
01:05:21,739 --> 01:05:22,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ja njih pitam, pa gde je on spava?

2288
01:05:22,920 --> 01:05:24,639
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kažu, pa na brodima.

2289
01:05:24,639 --> 01:05:25,460
[SPEAKER_01] Nema brodova,

2290
01:05:25,460 --> 01:05:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] nema hridina,

2291
01:05:26,099 --> 01:05:26,659
[SPEAKER_01] samo je more.

2292
01:05:26,739 --> 01:05:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] gde je spava, umoranje.

2293
01:05:27,639 --> 01:05:29,179
[SPEAKER_01] Kažu, oni pa na moru.

2294
01:05:29,179 --> 01:05:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Odlično.

2295
01:05:30,000 --> 01:05:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] A šta ako je more nemirno?

2296
01:05:31,619 --> 01:05:36,179
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kažu, oni spava dok leti.

2297
01:05:36,179 --> 01:05:38,059
[SPEAKER_01] I šta je 40?

2298
01:05:38,059 --> 01:05:41,719
[SPEAKER_01] Pa leti, spava pri brzini

2299
01:05:41,719 --> 01:05:43,960
[SPEAKER_01] 40 km na sat.

2300
01:05:43,960 --> 01:05:46,159
[SPEAKER_01] Albatros ima autopilot,

2301
01:05:46,159 --> 01:05:47,159
[SPEAKER_01] kako zatvori oči,

2302
01:05:47,159 --> 01:05:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] on leti tom brzinom.

2303
01:05:48,699 --> 01:05:49,739
[SPEAKER_01] I sad je to jasno.

2304
01:05:49,739 --> 01:05:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je meni važno?

2305
01:05:50,760 --> 01:05:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Odgovor ili put do odgovora?

2306
01:05:52,539 --> 01:05:53,340
[SPEAKER_01] Pa put.

2307
01:05:53,340 --> 01:05:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo sve okrenuli

2308
01:05:55,420 --> 01:05:56,659
[SPEAKER_01] u školskom tom,

2309
01:05:56,659 --> 01:05:58,039
[SPEAKER_01] u metodologiji,

2310
01:05:58,039 --> 01:05:59,800
[SPEAKER_01] da bi dobili misle one procese

2311
01:05:59,800 --> 01:06:00,320
[SPEAKER_01] i smeh.

2312
01:06:00,320 --> 01:06:04,159
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

2313
01:06:04,159 --> 01:06:05,860
[SPEAKER_02] Sad,

2314
01:06:05,860 --> 01:06:07,000
[SPEAKER_02] evo,

2315
01:06:07,000 --> 01:06:09,199
[SPEAKER_02] kako nam se u zadnjih par desetljeća

2316
01:06:09,199 --> 01:06:09,800
[SPEAKER_02] životni stil

2317
01:06:09,800 --> 01:06:10,860
[SPEAKER_02] drastično promijenio?

2318
01:06:11,639 --> 01:06:12,760
[SPEAKER_02] Vjerovatno će nam se toliko

2319
01:06:12,760 --> 01:06:13,880
[SPEAKER_02] u sljedećih deset godina

2320
01:06:13,880 --> 01:06:14,480
[SPEAKER_02] promijeniti,

2321
01:06:14,480 --> 01:06:15,860
[SPEAKER_02] ako ne i pet godina,

2322
01:06:15,860 --> 01:06:17,880
[SPEAKER_02] kao u tih 40-50 godina priješnjih.

2323
01:06:17,880 --> 01:06:20,739
[SPEAKER_02] Da li vi osobno koristite

2324
01:06:20,739 --> 01:06:22,539
[SPEAKER_02] možda neke od ovih LLM-ova,

2325
01:06:22,539 --> 01:06:23,360
[SPEAKER_02] chat GPT,

2326
01:06:23,360 --> 01:06:26,219
[SPEAKER_02] geminaj, grok i tako dalje u svojom životu?

2327
01:06:26,219 --> 01:06:27,420
[SPEAKER_01] Koristim chat GPT,

2328
01:06:27,420 --> 01:06:28,599
[SPEAKER_01] eto neke podatke,

2329
01:06:28,599 --> 01:06:30,199
[SPEAKER_01] mrzim je da tražim po Google,

2330
01:06:30,199 --> 01:06:31,019
[SPEAKER_01] pa samo pitam.

2331
01:06:31,019 --> 01:06:31,719
[SPEAKER_01] Zna sve.

2332
01:06:31,719 --> 01:06:32,920
[SPEAKER_01] I to je sad,

2333
01:06:32,920 --> 01:06:34,099
[SPEAKER_01] ali nekad i slaže.

2334
01:06:34,099 --> 01:06:35,539
[SPEAKER_01] Onda mi to nije neki osnovan.

2335
01:06:35,539 --> 01:06:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] Onda moram da proverim.

2336
01:06:36,659 --> 01:06:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa onda gubim vreme.

2337
01:06:38,300 --> 01:06:39,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ovde je pojento o nečem u drugom.

2338
01:06:39,940 --> 01:06:42,820
[SPEAKER_01] Naš mozak ima određenu brzinu

2339
01:06:42,820 --> 01:06:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] kako radi.

2340
01:06:43,380 --> 01:06:46,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ja moram da kažemo da radi 25 na sat.

2341
01:06:46,159 --> 01:06:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, prijima 25 slika u sekundi,

2342
01:06:48,840 --> 01:06:50,159
[SPEAKER_01] pa ću reći 25 na sat.

2343
01:06:50,159 --> 01:06:51,940
[SPEAKER_01] Kad je neka opasnost,

2344
01:06:51,940 --> 01:06:54,659
[SPEAKER_01] mozak radi 100 ili 200 na sat.

2345
01:06:54,659 --> 01:06:56,639
[SPEAKER_01] I to je biološko ilimitirano.

2346
01:06:56,639 --> 01:06:57,739
[SPEAKER_01] A kompjuter?

2347
01:06:57,739 --> 01:06:59,860
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki je nov mikročip.

2348
01:06:59,860 --> 01:07:01,099
[SPEAKER_01] Brzina rada.

2349
01:07:01,099 --> 01:07:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] Sad je već hiljedu milijardi u sekundi.

2350
01:07:03,800 --> 01:07:05,460
[SPEAKER_01] Šta to znači?

2351
01:07:06,679 --> 01:07:08,860
[SPEAKER_01] Pa dok mi osmislimo šta treba da uredimo,

2352
01:07:08,860 --> 01:07:10,940
[SPEAKER_01] kompjuter ima već milijon kombinacija

2353
01:07:10,940 --> 01:07:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] za 0, 0, 0, 1 sekund.

2354
01:07:13,579 --> 01:07:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] 100 i onda najbolju jednu.

2355
01:07:16,380 --> 01:07:18,659
[SPEAKER_01] Či brzo će donositi odluke.

2356
01:07:18,659 --> 01:07:20,539
[SPEAKER_01] Naša je prednost.

2357
01:07:20,539 --> 01:07:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] Tu ispitujemo,

2358
01:07:21,820 --> 01:07:24,460
[SPEAKER_01] kompjuter nema visoko rezonovanje

2359
01:07:24,460 --> 01:07:26,400
[SPEAKER_01] i nema te nelogične priče.

2360
01:07:27,739 --> 01:07:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] I tu je još jedna načina za razviju kreatinosti

2361
01:07:30,539 --> 01:07:31,559
[SPEAKER_01] i nelogične priče.

2362
01:07:31,559 --> 01:07:34,480
[SPEAKER_01] Znači moramo da učimo periodu šeste godine.

2363
01:07:34,480 --> 01:07:37,480
[SPEAKER_01] Da učimo roditelje kako su dete razve,

2364
01:07:37,480 --> 01:07:38,360
[SPEAKER_01] da učimo vrtiće.

2365
01:07:38,360 --> 01:07:40,679
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo da vidimo te asociacije,

2366
01:07:40,679 --> 01:07:41,760
[SPEAKER_01] kako mozak radi,

2367
01:07:41,760 --> 01:07:42,840
[SPEAKER_01] iščekivanje,

2368
01:07:42,840 --> 01:07:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] šta znači hormoni,

2369
01:07:44,119 --> 01:07:45,599
[SPEAKER_01] oni su važni za učenje.

2370
01:07:45,599 --> 01:07:47,639
[SPEAKER_01] I dolazimo do toga,

2371
01:07:47,639 --> 01:07:49,639
[SPEAKER_01] pa moramo promeniti još nešto.

2372
01:07:49,639 --> 01:07:51,619
[SPEAKER_01] Da vratimo nelogične priče.

2373
01:07:52,599 --> 01:07:55,320
[SPEAKER_01] Mi nemamo proti kompjutera šanse pobeđunost.

2374
01:07:55,320 --> 01:07:56,760
[SPEAKER_01] Ja koristim, ja to vidim.

2375
01:07:56,760 --> 01:07:58,099
[SPEAKER_01] To jako brzo ide.

2376
01:07:58,099 --> 01:08:02,539
[SPEAKER_01] I ako mi sad imamo brzino našeg mozga limitiranu,

2377
01:08:02,539 --> 01:08:04,480
[SPEAKER_01] a kompjutere nemaju,

2378
01:08:04,480 --> 01:08:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] šta da radimo?

2379
01:08:07,239 --> 01:08:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] Učimo na pamet.

2380
01:08:08,099 --> 01:08:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] Pa evo samo jedan što stano govorim podate

2381
01:08:11,440 --> 01:08:13,880
[SPEAKER_01] kod deset najtraženih zanimanja danas.

2382
01:08:13,880 --> 01:08:16,380
[SPEAKER_01] Devetni je postalo od 2019.

2383
01:08:16,380 --> 01:08:20,420
[SPEAKER_01] I šta je onda funkcija obrazovnog sistema

2384
01:08:20,420 --> 01:08:22,079
[SPEAKER_01] da ih učimo da misle,

2385
01:08:22,600 --> 01:08:24,720
[SPEAKER_01] ili da znaju na pamet.

2386
01:08:24,720 --> 01:08:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] I tu smo došli do odvora.

2387
01:08:26,300 --> 01:08:27,880
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo da ih učimo da misle.

2388
01:08:27,880 --> 01:08:29,279
[SPEAKER_01] I taj mislni proces,

2389
01:08:29,279 --> 01:08:30,680
[SPEAKER_01] i aktivacija mozga,

2390
01:08:30,680 --> 01:08:31,960
[SPEAKER_01] a kad se na volje aktivira,

2391
01:08:31,960 --> 01:08:33,159
[SPEAKER_01] pa sad smo dobili,

2392
01:08:33,159 --> 01:08:33,899
[SPEAKER_01] imamo istrživanje,

2393
01:08:33,899 --> 01:08:35,880
[SPEAKER_01] radio sam nelogične priče.

2394
01:08:35,880 --> 01:08:38,100
[SPEAKER_01] Dajte malo da radimo ono što

2395
01:08:38,100 --> 01:08:40,520
[SPEAKER_01] nije bilo u našem sistemu prepoznato

2396
01:08:40,520 --> 01:08:42,760
[SPEAKER_01] kao što je nelogična priča.

2397
01:08:42,760 --> 01:08:44,579
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam se sa tim sustetao priput

2398
01:08:44,579 --> 01:08:46,880
[SPEAKER_01] već više od deset godina u Sloveniji.

2399
01:08:46,880 --> 01:08:48,859
[SPEAKER_01] Imao sam stih u Velenju,

2400
01:08:48,859 --> 01:08:50,039
[SPEAKER_01] u vrtiću sam bio.

2401
01:08:51,140 --> 01:08:52,960
[SPEAKER_01] Naša mama bi u svet odletela.

2402
01:08:52,960 --> 01:08:54,859
[SPEAKER_01] I sad kažem,

2403
01:08:54,859 --> 01:08:55,479
[SPEAKER_01] nacrtajte.

2404
01:08:55,479 --> 01:08:58,960
[SPEAKER_01] Šta su odrasle osobe nacrtale?

2405
01:08:58,960 --> 01:09:00,500
[SPEAKER_01] Mama u avionu.

2406
01:09:00,500 --> 01:09:03,500
[SPEAKER_01] Mama na aerodromu.

2407
01:09:03,500 --> 01:09:05,079
[SPEAKER_01] I to je to.

2408
01:09:05,079 --> 01:09:07,380
[SPEAKER_01] A kad smo dali decu od 5-6 godina,

2409
01:09:07,380 --> 01:09:08,100
[SPEAKER_01] šta sam dobio?

2410
01:09:08,100 --> 01:09:09,520
[SPEAKER_01] Mama na oblaku.

2411
01:09:09,520 --> 01:09:11,899
[SPEAKER_01] Mama sa krilima iz glave.

2412
01:09:13,060 --> 01:09:14,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ja gledam, to je to.

2413
01:09:14,079 --> 01:09:15,739
[SPEAKER_01] I nosim na moje fakulte,

2414
01:09:15,739 --> 01:09:16,520
[SPEAKER_01] bio sam uljubljani,

2415
01:09:16,520 --> 01:09:17,300
[SPEAKER_01] sad sam u kopriju.

2416
01:09:17,300 --> 01:09:18,380
[SPEAKER_01] Pokazim kolegama.

2417
01:09:18,380 --> 01:09:19,840
[SPEAKER_01] Oduševljen.

2418
01:09:19,840 --> 01:09:21,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, šta si to radio?

2419
01:09:21,300 --> 01:09:23,720
[SPEAKER_01] Pitam, pa šta je bilo?

2420
01:09:23,720 --> 01:09:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] To ne može, pitam.

2421
01:09:25,000 --> 01:09:25,600
[SPEAKER_01] Što ne može?

2422
01:09:25,600 --> 01:09:26,960
[SPEAKER_01] Pa to ne može.

2423
01:09:26,960 --> 01:09:28,640
[SPEAKER_01] Kako mogu krila da rastu iz glave?

2424
01:09:28,640 --> 01:09:30,619
[SPEAKER_01] I sad ne dam ja

2425
01:09:30,619 --> 01:09:32,520
[SPEAKER_01] i kažem učiteljima,

2426
01:09:32,520 --> 01:09:34,300
[SPEAKER_01] borite se srcem ono što znate,

2427
01:09:34,300 --> 01:09:35,520
[SPEAKER_01] što verite, borite se.

2428
01:09:36,060 --> 01:09:38,159
[SPEAKER_01] Kažem, pa zna dete da krila

2429
01:09:38,159 --> 01:09:39,399
[SPEAKER_01] ne mogu da rastu iz glave.

2430
01:09:39,399 --> 01:09:40,859
[SPEAKER_01] Pustite ga da rastu.

2431
01:09:40,859 --> 01:09:43,439
[SPEAKER_01] Pitam je zašto.

2432
01:09:43,439 --> 01:09:45,220
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ako ne mogu krila iz glave,

2433
01:09:45,220 --> 01:09:46,359
[SPEAKER_01] ne može mama na oblaku.

2434
01:09:46,359 --> 01:09:48,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ako je to glupo i to ne može.

2435
01:09:48,500 --> 01:09:50,100
[SPEAKER_01] Mi njima zatvaramo

2436
01:09:50,100 --> 01:09:51,760
[SPEAKER_01] asociativne regije.

2437
01:09:51,760 --> 01:09:53,340
[SPEAKER_01] To je 30% mozga.

2438
01:09:53,340 --> 01:09:54,560
[SPEAKER_01] A šta se tu nalazi?

2439
01:09:54,560 --> 01:09:55,859
[SPEAKER_01] Kreativnost.

2440
01:09:55,859 --> 01:09:58,319
[SPEAKER_01] I možda još važnije divergentno mišljenje,

2441
01:09:58,319 --> 01:09:59,500
[SPEAKER_01] to je darovitost.

2442
01:09:59,500 --> 01:10:01,180
[SPEAKER_01] Zato se često kaže

2443
01:10:01,180 --> 01:10:03,079
[SPEAKER_01] da škola ubija kreativnost.

2444
01:10:04,420 --> 01:10:05,819
[SPEAKER_01] Onda smo malo pričali

2445
01:10:05,819 --> 01:10:06,800
[SPEAKER_01] da ne može, može,

2446
01:10:06,800 --> 01:10:07,479
[SPEAKER_01] ja se s njima.

2447
01:10:07,479 --> 01:10:09,739
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to je dobra diskusija sa kolegama

2448
01:10:09,739 --> 01:10:12,060
[SPEAKER_01] kad vi pričate argumentima.

2449
01:10:12,060 --> 01:10:13,220
[SPEAKER_01] Dok recimo,

2450
01:10:13,220 --> 01:10:14,960
[SPEAKER_01] imate čestu situaciju

2451
01:10:14,960 --> 01:10:17,079
[SPEAKER_01] da neki šef katrile kaže

2452
01:10:17,079 --> 01:10:17,659
[SPEAKER_01] to ne može.

2453
01:10:17,659 --> 01:10:19,100
[SPEAKER_01] Nemo diskusija,

2454
01:10:19,100 --> 01:10:19,899
[SPEAKER_01] nema argumenta,

2455
01:10:19,899 --> 01:10:20,899
[SPEAKER_01] tu smo mi zarobljeni,

2456
01:10:20,899 --> 01:10:21,720
[SPEAKER_01] idemo nazad.

2457
01:10:21,720 --> 01:10:23,180
[SPEAKER_01] I onda se ja svetim

2458
01:10:23,180 --> 01:10:25,300
[SPEAKER_01] ima pesman Otona Župančića,

2459
01:10:25,300 --> 01:10:26,500
[SPEAKER_01] Lenka se šeta,

2460
01:10:26,500 --> 01:10:27,260
[SPEAKER_01] metla po metu.

2461
01:10:27,260 --> 01:10:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, kad bi prevelio,

2462
01:10:28,619 --> 01:10:29,180
[SPEAKER_01] to bi bilo

2463
01:10:29,180 --> 01:10:30,699
[SPEAKER_01] dok se Lenka šeta,

2464
01:10:30,699 --> 01:10:31,720
[SPEAKER_01] metla sama mete.

2465
01:10:31,720 --> 01:10:33,659
[SPEAKER_01] I ja pitan te kolege,

2466
01:10:34,300 --> 01:10:35,600
[SPEAKER_01] koja metla sama mete.

2467
01:10:35,600 --> 01:10:37,460
[SPEAKER_01] Kažu,

2468
01:10:37,460 --> 01:10:38,180
[SPEAKER_01] oni nijedna.

2469
01:10:38,180 --> 01:10:39,300
[SPEAKER_01] Pa zabranio

2470
01:10:39,300 --> 01:10:40,220
[SPEAKER_01] Otona Župančića,

2471
01:10:40,220 --> 01:10:41,239
[SPEAKER_01] izbacite ga iz lektire.

2472
01:10:41,239 --> 01:10:42,720
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su se nasmijeli,

2473
01:10:42,720 --> 01:10:44,279
[SPEAKER_01] e sad je to u okviru

2474
01:10:44,279 --> 01:10:44,880
[SPEAKER_01] kurikulum,

2475
01:10:44,880 --> 01:10:45,880
[SPEAKER_01] a to u prednjem studentim

2476
01:10:45,880 --> 01:10:46,439
[SPEAKER_01] u Sloveniji.

2477
01:10:46,439 --> 01:10:47,720
[SPEAKER_01] Nelogične priče.

2478
01:10:47,720 --> 01:10:48,500
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je došao

2479
01:10:48,500 --> 01:10:49,960
[SPEAKER_01] profesor Fischer iz Berlina,

