[SPEAKER_01] Po 100%.

3150
01:23:38,460 --> 01:23:39,460
[SPEAKER_01] Pa dajte da teorije

3151
01:23:39,460 --> 01:23:40,479
[SPEAKER_01] koje koristimo malo

3152
01:23:40,479 --> 01:23:42,119
[SPEAKER_01] dodamo iz našeg okruženja.

3153
01:23:42,119 --> 01:23:42,979
[SPEAKER_01] To ću sad raditi

3154
01:23:42,979 --> 01:23:44,680
[SPEAKER_01] na učiteljskom fakultetu

3155
01:23:44,680 --> 01:23:45,159
[SPEAKER_01] u Zagrebu.

3156
01:23:45,159 --> 01:23:46,479
[SPEAKER_01] Dajte da mi vidimo

3157
01:23:46,479 --> 01:23:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] kako mozak radi,

3158
01:23:47,460 --> 01:23:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] kako se aktiviraju

3159
01:23:48,699 --> 01:23:49,260
[SPEAKER_01] te regije.

3160
01:23:49,260 --> 01:23:50,439
[SPEAKER_01] Dajte da uzmemo teorije

3161
01:23:50,439 --> 01:23:51,520
[SPEAKER_01] koje postoje pa da dodamo

3162
01:23:51,520 --> 01:23:52,800
[SPEAKER_01] nešto iz našeg okruženja.

3163
01:23:52,800 --> 01:23:54,180
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ako budemo koristili

3164
01:23:54,180 --> 01:23:55,260
[SPEAKER_01] tuzje teorije

3165
01:23:55,260 --> 01:23:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] bez ikakve promjene,

3166
01:23:56,800 --> 01:23:58,199
[SPEAKER_01] nema tu naprijed.

3167
01:23:58,199 --> 01:23:59,319
[SPEAKER_01] Promjenilo se okruženje.

3168
01:23:59,319 --> 01:24:00,600
[SPEAKER_01] Mora brže da se radi.

3169
01:24:00,600 --> 01:24:03,039
[SPEAKER_02] A što je

3170
01:24:03,039 --> 01:24:04,239
[SPEAKER_02] od svega ovoga

3171
01:24:04,239 --> 01:24:05,180
[SPEAKER_02] što ste rekli do sada,

3172
01:24:05,180 --> 01:24:06,340
[SPEAKER_02] što je primjenjivo

3173
01:24:06,340 --> 01:24:07,000
[SPEAKER_02] za roditelje?

3174
01:24:07,000 --> 01:24:08,279
[SPEAKER_02] To je što je primjenjivo

3175
01:24:08,279 --> 01:24:09,180
[SPEAKER_02] za odrasle?

3176
01:24:09,180 --> 01:24:10,600
[SPEAKER_02] Evo roditelj odmah.

3177
01:24:10,600 --> 01:24:11,399
[SPEAKER_02] Posljedan da ovo sve

3178
01:24:11,399 --> 01:24:12,460
[SPEAKER_02] primjenjivo je na odrasle.

3179
01:24:12,460 --> 01:24:12,819
[SPEAKER_01] Pre zaštisivanje.

3180
01:24:12,819 --> 01:24:13,220
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

3181
01:24:13,220 --> 01:24:14,340
[SPEAKER_01] Pre zaštisivanje je grešo.

3182
01:24:14,340 --> 01:24:15,319
[SPEAKER_02] Mislim od ove igre

3183
01:24:15,319 --> 01:24:16,340
[SPEAKER_02] od kreativnosti.

3184
01:24:16,340 --> 01:24:16,359
[SPEAKER_02] Odmah ću reći.

3185
01:24:16,359 --> 01:24:17,640
[SPEAKER_02] Idemo sad da je od rođenja

3186
01:24:17,640 --> 01:24:19,319
[SPEAKER_01] do trece, do pete za roditelje

3187
01:24:19,319 --> 01:24:21,220
[SPEAKER_01] pre zaštisivanje je štetno.

3188
01:24:21,220 --> 01:24:23,380
[SPEAKER_01] Pustite dete da padne,

3189
01:24:23,380 --> 01:24:24,500
[SPEAKER_01] ali ne na betonu,

3190
01:24:24,500 --> 01:24:25,100
[SPEAKER_01] na livadi,

3191
01:24:25,100 --> 01:24:26,720
[SPEAKER_01] pa na dve ruke,

3192
01:24:26,720 --> 01:24:27,359
[SPEAKER_01] pa na jednu,

3193
01:24:27,359 --> 01:24:28,000
[SPEAKER_01] pa na lakat,

3194
01:24:28,000 --> 01:24:28,899
[SPEAKER_01] neka padne.

3195
01:24:28,899 --> 01:24:30,460
[SPEAKER_01] Pustite kada se vrti.

3196
01:24:30,460 --> 01:24:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] Ne po stepenicama,

3197
01:24:31,840 --> 01:24:33,220
[SPEAKER_01] nego po parketu,

3198
01:24:33,220 --> 01:24:33,800
[SPEAKER_01] po tepihu,

3199
01:24:33,800 --> 01:24:34,380
[SPEAKER_01] na livadi.

3200
01:24:34,380 --> 01:24:36,220
[SPEAKER_01] Znači dete mora da se vrti,

3201
01:24:36,220 --> 01:24:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] da skače,

3202
01:24:36,800 --> 01:24:37,600
[SPEAKER_01] da se kreće.

3203
01:24:37,600 --> 01:24:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] Pre zaštisivanje

3204
01:24:40,199 --> 01:24:41,220
[SPEAKER_01] ošteće dete.

3205
01:24:41,220 --> 01:24:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] Znači nema one

3206
01:24:42,000 --> 01:24:42,819
[SPEAKER_01] pazi pašćiš.

3207
01:24:42,819 --> 01:24:44,539
[SPEAKER_01] Pa može,

3208
01:24:44,539 --> 01:24:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] ako je po stepenicama

3209
01:24:45,739 --> 01:24:46,840
[SPEAKER_01] se zatrčalo dete,

3210
01:24:47,000 --> 01:24:48,420
[SPEAKER_01] a moramo da ga vodimo

3211
01:24:48,420 --> 01:24:49,779
[SPEAKER_01] da je prirodno park.

3212
01:24:49,779 --> 01:24:51,020
[SPEAKER_01] Je li tako?

3213
01:24:51,020 --> 01:24:51,460
[SPEAKER_01] Livada.

3214
01:24:51,460 --> 01:24:53,239
[SPEAKER_01] Tu neka padne.

3215
01:24:53,239 --> 01:24:54,140
[SPEAKER_01] Onda dalje.

3216
01:24:54,140 --> 01:24:55,279
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo,

3217
01:24:55,279 --> 01:24:57,180
[SPEAKER_01] rana stimulacija kognitivna,

3218
01:24:57,180 --> 01:24:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] da aktiviram asocijtene regije,

3219
01:24:58,739 --> 01:24:59,600
[SPEAKER_01] nelogične priječe,

3220
01:24:59,600 --> 01:25:00,520
[SPEAKER_01] čitajte im bajke.

3221
01:25:00,520 --> 01:25:02,619
[SPEAKER_01] Izmislite bajku.

3222
01:25:02,619 --> 01:25:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] Kako?

3223
01:25:04,340 --> 01:25:05,600
[SPEAKER_01] Pa izmislite bajku.

3224
01:25:05,600 --> 01:25:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] U prijativo.

3225
01:25:06,500 --> 01:25:07,619
[SPEAKER_01] Izmislite ću u školi

3226
01:25:07,619 --> 01:25:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] i u Andrići Zagreba.

3227
01:25:08,960 --> 01:25:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] Znači dajte im nelogične priječe,

3228
01:25:11,119 --> 01:25:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] izmislite bajku,

3229
01:25:12,079 --> 01:25:13,020
[SPEAKER_01] pričite bajke,

3230
01:25:13,020 --> 01:25:14,680
[SPEAKER_01] dajte im sakrivanje reči.

3231
01:25:14,680 --> 01:25:16,100
[SPEAKER_01] Kompas pas.

3232
01:25:16,779 --> 01:25:17,720
[SPEAKER_01] To je najlakši nivo.

3233
01:25:17,720 --> 01:25:19,220
[SPEAKER_01] Koji životinju reči?

3234
01:25:19,220 --> 01:25:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] Kompas pas.

3235
01:25:20,079 --> 01:25:21,260
[SPEAKER_01] A što je malo teže?

3236
01:25:21,260 --> 01:25:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] Već za prvi i drugi razred.

3237
01:25:22,800 --> 01:25:24,079
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo je bilo za vrtiće.

3238
01:25:24,079 --> 01:25:25,020
[SPEAKER_01] A za prvi i drugi,

3239
01:25:25,020 --> 01:25:29,020
[SPEAKER_01] koji čovekov prijatelj

3240
01:25:29,020 --> 01:25:30,560
[SPEAKER_01] se nalazi u reči kompas?

3241
01:25:30,560 --> 01:25:32,720
[SPEAKER_01] Pas.

3242
01:25:32,720 --> 01:25:34,520
[SPEAKER_01] A još teže pitanje

3243
01:25:34,520 --> 01:25:35,479
[SPEAKER_01] za drugi i treći razred.

3244
01:25:35,479 --> 01:25:37,239
[SPEAKER_01] Koji čovekov prijatelj

3245
01:25:37,239 --> 01:25:38,300
[SPEAKER_01] se nalazi u nečemu

3246
01:25:38,300 --> 01:25:39,060
[SPEAKER_01] što nam pomože

3247
01:25:39,060 --> 01:25:40,060
[SPEAKER_01] za orijentaciju?

3248
01:25:41,359 --> 01:25:43,180
[SPEAKER_01] To su mislni procesi.

3249
01:25:43,180 --> 01:25:44,439
[SPEAKER_01] Orientacija,

3250
01:25:44,439 --> 01:25:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] kompas,

3251
01:25:45,000 --> 01:25:45,439
[SPEAKER_01] prijatelj,

3252
01:25:45,439 --> 01:25:45,739
[SPEAKER_01] pas,

3253
01:25:45,739 --> 01:25:46,100
[SPEAKER_01] kompas,

3254
01:25:46,100 --> 01:25:46,359
[SPEAKER_01] pas.

3255
01:25:46,359 --> 01:25:47,739
[SPEAKER_01] Znači isto je pitanje

3256
01:25:47,739 --> 01:25:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] za vrtić za školu

3257
01:25:49,159 --> 01:25:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] i za peti razred.

3258
01:25:50,119 --> 01:25:51,600
[SPEAKER_01] Što je meni cilj?

3259
01:25:51,600 --> 01:25:52,439
[SPEAKER_01] Rekao sam,

3260
01:25:52,439 --> 01:25:54,100
[SPEAKER_01] doni mene naprave pitanje.

3261
01:25:54,100 --> 01:25:55,420
[SPEAKER_01] I oni tada koriste

3262
01:25:55,420 --> 01:25:56,340
[SPEAKER_01] školskog rade,

3263
01:25:56,340 --> 01:25:57,020
[SPEAKER_01] uzimaju,

3264
01:25:57,020 --> 01:25:58,319
[SPEAKER_01] prave mi pitanje,

3265
01:25:58,319 --> 01:25:59,039
[SPEAKER_01] što su radili,

3266
01:25:59,039 --> 01:26:00,439
[SPEAKER_01] ponučili su lekciju,

3267
01:26:00,439 --> 01:26:01,060
[SPEAKER_01] ključne reči,

3268
01:26:01,060 --> 01:26:01,819
[SPEAKER_01] još su i mislili.

3269
01:26:02,819 --> 01:26:03,520
[SPEAKER_01] A što je suprotno?

3270
01:26:03,520 --> 01:26:05,140
[SPEAKER_01] Duče na pameti da zaboravi.

3271
01:26:05,140 --> 01:26:07,199
[SPEAKER_01] Znači to je za roditelje

3272
01:26:07,199 --> 01:26:08,399
[SPEAKER_01] nelogične priječe

3273
01:26:08,399 --> 01:26:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] sa krivanje reči

3274
01:26:09,239 --> 01:26:10,220
[SPEAKER_01] onda dolazi škola.

3275
01:26:10,220 --> 01:26:12,640
[SPEAKER_01] Onda moramo gradivo

3276
01:26:12,640 --> 01:26:15,159
[SPEAKER_01] da stavljamo funkciju

3277
01:26:15,159 --> 01:26:15,739
[SPEAKER_01] razmiješljenja

3278
01:26:15,739 --> 01:26:16,720
[SPEAKER_01] kao što su vijalvatros.

3279
01:26:16,720 --> 01:26:18,239
[SPEAKER_01] Da oni misle

3280
01:26:18,239 --> 01:26:19,500
[SPEAKER_01] i oni naučaju puno toga.

3281
01:26:19,500 --> 01:26:20,439
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže neko,

3282
01:26:20,439 --> 01:26:22,520
[SPEAKER_01] a kako onda nauče matematiku

3283
01:26:22,520 --> 01:26:23,060
[SPEAKER_01] i to može,

3284
01:26:23,060 --> 01:26:23,840
[SPEAKER_01] sad smo radili,

3285
01:26:23,840 --> 01:26:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] firma Kleti uzela neku našu igračku,

3286
01:26:27,000 --> 01:26:28,119
[SPEAKER_01] djeca si igruju

3287
01:26:28,119 --> 01:26:29,260
[SPEAKER_01] i nauče tablice omloženja,

3288
01:26:29,260 --> 01:26:29,819
[SPEAKER_01] može i to,

3289
01:26:29,819 --> 01:26:30,800
[SPEAKER_01] rimske brojeve,

3290
01:26:30,859 --> 01:26:31,699
[SPEAKER_01] tablice omloženja.

3291
01:26:31,699 --> 01:26:34,119
[SPEAKER_01] Neke stvari će morati

3292
01:26:34,119 --> 01:26:35,100
[SPEAKER_01] da nauče na pamet.

3293
01:26:35,100 --> 01:26:36,819
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako je mozak utreniran

3294
01:26:36,819 --> 01:26:37,699
[SPEAKER_01] da stalno misli,

3295
01:26:37,699 --> 01:26:39,039
[SPEAKER_01] nauče će i na pamet.

3296
01:26:39,039 --> 01:26:40,720
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako je sve morio na pamet,

3297
01:26:40,720 --> 01:26:41,899
[SPEAKER_01] ne ide to.

3298
01:26:41,899 --> 01:26:42,979
[SPEAKER_01] Ne može.

3299
01:26:42,979 --> 01:26:44,939
[SPEAKER_01] I sad kad sam pričao

3300
01:26:44,939 --> 01:26:45,859
[SPEAKER_01] te nelogične priječe,

3301
01:26:45,859 --> 01:26:47,140
[SPEAKER_01] opet ću se vratiti na njih.

3302
01:26:47,140 --> 01:26:49,819
[SPEAKER_01] Bili su iz Hong Konga

3303
01:26:49,819 --> 01:26:52,520
[SPEAKER_01] da bi oni radili NTC,

3304
01:26:52,520 --> 01:26:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] pa je bila delegacija,

3305
01:26:53,800 --> 01:26:54,520
[SPEAKER_01] pa su provovali

3306
01:26:54,520 --> 01:26:55,939
[SPEAKER_01] dva puta sveć bili hod nas

3307
01:26:55,939 --> 01:26:56,899
[SPEAKER_01] i oni gledaju

3308
01:26:56,899 --> 01:26:58,000
[SPEAKER_01] djecu kako se smiju

3309
01:26:58,000 --> 01:26:59,180
[SPEAKER_01] kad su nelogične priječe.

3310
01:27:00,720 --> 01:27:03,260
[SPEAKER_01] Kao bi dozvoljete

3311
01:27:03,260 --> 01:27:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] da se smiju u školi.

3312
01:27:04,539 --> 01:27:05,840
[SPEAKER_01] Pitan, što da ne?

3313
01:27:05,840 --> 01:27:09,420
[SPEAKER_01] Kao to je škola?

3314
01:27:09,420 --> 01:27:11,279
[SPEAKER_01] Kao to ne može.

3315
01:27:11,279 --> 01:27:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] Počeli i oni

3316
01:27:13,039 --> 01:27:14,340
[SPEAKER_01] drugi dan da se smiju,

3317
01:27:14,340 --> 01:27:15,840
[SPEAKER_01] jer su videli šta je to.

3318
01:27:15,840 --> 01:27:17,399
[SPEAKER_01] I tada nam kažu,

3319
01:27:17,399 --> 01:27:18,300
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam bio u šoku,

3320
01:27:18,300 --> 01:27:20,439
[SPEAKER_01] da oni imaju metode

3321
01:27:20,439 --> 01:27:22,159
[SPEAKER_01] učenja vikanjem.

3322
01:27:23,600 --> 01:27:24,039
[SPEAKER_01] vikanje?

3323
01:27:24,039 --> 01:27:24,439
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

3324
01:27:24,439 --> 01:27:26,140
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kako?

3325
01:27:26,140 --> 01:27:28,239
[SPEAKER_01] Pa primetili su kad učitelj

3326
01:27:28,239 --> 01:27:29,760
[SPEAKER_01] vikne da deto upamti.

3327
01:27:29,760 --> 01:27:31,340
[SPEAKER_01] Pa su onda razvili

3328
01:27:31,340 --> 01:27:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] celu metodu

3329
01:27:32,119 --> 01:27:34,600
[SPEAKER_01] kako viće sa raširanim rukama,

3330
01:27:34,600 --> 01:27:35,859
[SPEAKER_01] po dijagonali,

3331
01:27:35,859 --> 01:27:36,739
[SPEAKER_01] ispred deteta,

3332
01:27:36,739 --> 01:27:37,560
[SPEAKER_01] u polu,

3333
01:27:37,560 --> 01:27:37,939
[SPEAKER_01] u čučnju,

3334
01:27:37,939 --> 01:27:39,199
[SPEAKER_01] gledamo dete u rame,

3335
01:27:39,199 --> 01:27:40,060
[SPEAKER_01] u lakat, u oči.

3336
01:27:40,060 --> 01:27:41,279
[SPEAKER_01] Ja njih slušam

3337
01:27:41,279 --> 01:27:43,199
[SPEAKER_01] i pitam,

3338
01:27:43,199 --> 01:27:45,039
[SPEAKER_01] pa znate koja je funkcija

3339
01:27:45,039 --> 01:27:46,220
[SPEAKER_01] vikanja u fiziologiji?

3340
01:27:46,220 --> 01:27:48,979
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kao ne?

3341
01:27:48,979 --> 01:27:50,579
[SPEAKER_01] I ovo je za roditelje.

3342
01:27:50,579 --> 01:27:52,199
[SPEAKER_01] I još jedan savet.

3343
01:27:52,199 --> 01:27:54,699
[SPEAKER_01] Nemojte vikati na dete.

3344
01:27:54,699 --> 01:27:55,079
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

3345
01:27:55,079 --> 01:27:57,199
[SPEAKER_01] Vikanje služi za mozak.

3346
01:27:57,199 --> 01:27:58,939
[SPEAKER_01] Da ga zustavimo.

3347
01:27:58,939 --> 01:28:00,220
[SPEAKER_01] Jer mozak je organ

3348
01:28:00,220 --> 01:28:01,739
[SPEAKER_01] za preživljavanje.

3349
01:28:01,739 --> 01:28:03,199
[SPEAKER_01] Dete hoda,

3350
01:28:03,199 --> 01:28:04,079
[SPEAKER_01] ivicom provali,

3351
01:28:04,079 --> 01:28:05,199
[SPEAKER_01] stani, on stane.

3352
01:28:05,199 --> 01:28:06,680
[SPEAKER_01] Hoda po tankom ledu,

3353
01:28:06,680 --> 01:28:07,779
[SPEAKER_01] stani, dete stane.

3354
01:28:07,779 --> 01:28:08,979
[SPEAKER_01] Trči po parkingu,

3355
01:28:08,979 --> 01:28:10,140
[SPEAKER_01] stane, dete stane.

3356
01:28:11,020 --> 01:28:12,119
[SPEAKER_01] I dete uponti situaciju,

3357
01:28:12,119 --> 01:28:12,720
[SPEAKER_01] vikali smo,

3358
01:28:12,720 --> 01:28:13,560
[SPEAKER_01] uponti,

3359
01:28:13,560 --> 01:28:14,560
[SPEAKER_01] gde je to bilo

3360
01:28:14,560 --> 01:28:15,680
[SPEAKER_01] i više to neće raditi.

3361
01:28:15,680 --> 01:28:17,340
[SPEAKER_01] I tako čuvamo život

3362
01:28:17,340 --> 01:28:18,020
[SPEAKER_01] našeg deteta.

3363
01:28:18,020 --> 01:28:19,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ako vičemo svaki sekund,

