4043
01:42:09,500 --> 01:42:09,840
[SPEAKER_01] drugi,

4044
01:42:09,840 --> 01:42:10,260
[SPEAKER_01] treći.

4045
01:42:10,260 --> 01:42:11,659
[SPEAKER_01] On sanja do prekidi,

4046
01:42:11,659 --> 01:42:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] sanja dalje.

4047
01:42:12,500 --> 01:42:14,020
[SPEAKER_01] I vidi da je našo rješenje,

4048
01:42:14,020 --> 01:42:16,140
[SPEAKER_01] da je to dobit će nerešeno,

4049
01:42:16,140 --> 01:42:17,319
[SPEAKER_01] neće izgubiti.

4050
01:42:18,319 --> 01:42:18,960
[SPEAKER_01] probudi se,

4051
01:42:18,960 --> 01:42:19,479
[SPEAKER_01] to je to

4052
01:42:19,479 --> 01:42:20,819
[SPEAKER_01] i nastavi da spava.

4053
01:42:20,819 --> 01:42:21,399
[SPEAKER_01] Ujutro,

4054
01:42:21,399 --> 01:42:22,560
[SPEAKER_01] nema sna.

4055
01:42:22,560 --> 01:42:24,560
[SPEAKER_01] On pokuša da se seti,

4056
01:42:24,560 --> 01:42:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] ne može.

4057
01:42:24,960 --> 01:42:26,939
[SPEAKER_01] I svakodnosimo situaciju,

4058
01:42:26,939 --> 01:42:27,640
