[SPEAKER_01] ove njegovi pomoćnici,

4063
01:42:33,079 --> 01:42:34,020
[SPEAKER_01] isto vele majsturi,

4064
01:42:34,020 --> 01:42:35,420
[SPEAKER_01] celu noć su radili,

4065
01:42:35,420 --> 01:42:36,279
[SPEAKER_01] nemaj rešenja,

4066
01:42:36,279 --> 01:42:36,819
[SPEAKER_01] kažu,

4067
01:42:36,819 --> 01:42:38,479
[SPEAKER_01] Anatoli zovoga tolja,

4068
01:42:38,479 --> 01:42:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] ne znamo,

4069
01:42:40,199 --> 01:42:41,520
[SPEAKER_01] nemaj rešenja.

4070
01:42:41,520 --> 01:42:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kaže,

4071
01:42:42,579 --> 01:42:43,079
[SPEAKER_01] ima sanja,

4072
01:42:43,079 --> 01:42:43,680
[SPEAKER_01] sam pokažen,

4073
