4074
01:42:44,659 --> 01:42:46,819
[SPEAKER_01] On se vraća u sobu.

4075
01:42:47,699 --> 01:42:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] E sad da vidimo,

4076
01:42:48,380 --> 01:42:49,600
[SPEAKER_01] igra je pet sati,

4077
01:42:49,600 --> 01:42:51,359
[SPEAKER_01] sat i po,

4078
01:42:51,359 --> 01:42:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] je analizirao

4079
01:42:53,500 --> 01:42:54,340
