4084
01:43:00,039 --> 01:43:01,119
[SPEAKER_01] mozak je pod naponom,

4085
01:43:01,119 --> 01:43:01,960
[SPEAKER_01] mozak se budi.

4086
01:43:01,960 --> 01:43:03,000
[SPEAKER_01] On to sanja,

4087
