[SPEAKER_01] mozak je to odradio.

4088
01:43:03,979 --> 01:43:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] On se vraća u sobu,

4089
01:43:05,960 --> 01:43:06,979
[SPEAKER_01] ne može da se seti,

4090
01:43:06,979 --> 01:43:07,680
[SPEAKER_01] šta će čovek,

4091
01:43:07,680 --> 01:43:08,960
[SPEAKER_01] skjede su pjeđamo,

4092
01:43:08,960 --> 01:43:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] oprao zube,

4093
01:43:09,539 --> 01:43:11,060
[SPEAKER_01] lego kreve spustio u letnu

4094
01:43:11,060 --> 01:43:12,359
[SPEAKER_01] i pokuša da spavi,

4095
01:43:12,359 --> 01:43:14,039
[SPEAKER_01] u tih sati je po spava,

4096
01:43:14,039 --> 01:43:14,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne spava,

4097
01:43:14,619 --> 01:43:16,479
[SPEAKER_01] odjednom izađe san.

4098
01:43:17,020 --> 01:43:17,579
[SPEAKER_01] I to je to.

4099
01:43:17,579 --> 01:43:19,100
[SPEAKER_01] Odjegrao je,

4100
01:43:19,100 --> 01:43:20,199
[SPEAKER_01] izvukao nerešeno,

4101
