[SPEAKER_01] kasnije postao prvak sveti.

4102
01:43:22,079 --> 01:43:22,840
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže on meni,

4103
01:43:22,840 --> 01:43:24,020
[SPEAKER_01] od tog momenta,

4104
01:43:24,020 --> 01:43:26,180
[SPEAKER_01] pored kreveta su mi uvek

4105
01:43:26,180 --> 01:43:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] olovka i papir.

4106
01:43:27,340 --> 01:43:29,600
[SPEAKER_01] Ja često se posle desilo

4107
01:43:29,600 --> 01:43:31,359
[SPEAKER_01] da sanja da zapiše,

4108
01:43:31,359 --> 01:43:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] uvijesu se probude,

4109
01:43:32,659 --> 01:43:33,659
[SPEAKER_01] neće se da vidi papir.

4110
01:43:33,659 --> 01:43:34,880
[SPEAKER_01] Misli, misli,

4111
01:43:34,880 --> 01:43:35,560
[SPEAKER_01] ne ide, ne ide,

4112
01:43:35,560 --> 01:43:36,340
[SPEAKER_01] pogleda papiric,

4113
01:43:36,340 --> 01:43:37,199
[SPEAKER_01] pa da, to je to.

4114
01:43:38,340 --> 01:43:39,439
[SPEAKER_01] Niko ne zna

4115
01:43:39,439 --> 01:43:41,600
[SPEAKER_01] šta to mozak radi

4116
01:43:41,600 --> 01:43:42,520
[SPEAKER_01] u rem fazi.

4117
01:43:42,520 --> 01:43:44,560
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je jako važna.

4118
01:43:44,560 --> 01:43:45,859
[SPEAKER_01] Ona se čak zove

4119
01:43:45,859 --> 01:43:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] paradoksalna faza spavanja,

4120
01:43:47,380 --> 01:43:48,760
[SPEAKER_01] jer mozak je praktično

4121
01:43:48,760 --> 01:43:49,439
[SPEAKER_01] budniji,

4122
01:43:49,439 --> 01:43:51,060
[SPEAKER_01] budniji,

4123
01:43:51,060 --> 01:43:51,699
[SPEAKER_01] aktivniji

4124
01:43:51,699 --> 01:43:52,720
[SPEAKER_01] nego u budnom stanju.

4125
01:43:52,720 --> 01:43:54,739
[SPEAKER_01] To je još enigma.

4126
01:43:54,739 --> 01:43:55,899
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

4127
01:43:55,899 --> 01:43:57,180
[SPEAKER_01] rem faza je jako važna.

4128
01:43:57,180 --> 01:43:58,199
[SPEAKER_01] A šta sam rekao,

4129
01:43:58,199 --> 01:43:59,560
[SPEAKER_01] jesmo poremitili rem fazu

4130
01:43:59,560 --> 01:44:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] u našoj deci?

4131
01:44:00,079 --> 01:44:01,520
[SPEAKER_01] Da li mobilni telefon?

4132
01:44:01,520 --> 01:44:02,800
[SPEAKER_01] Okruženje se menja.

4133
01:44:03,140 --> 01:44:03,840
[SPEAKER_01] bit će našan deto

4134
01:44:03,840 --> 01:44:04,779
[SPEAKER_01] i to kao namo što bilo

4135
01:44:04,779 --> 01:44:05,359
[SPEAKER_01] neće.

4136
01:44:05,359 --> 01:44:06,560
[SPEAKER_01] Moramo da učimo.

4137
01:44:06,560 --> 01:44:10,020
[SPEAKER_01] Uživao se.

4138
01:44:10,020 --> 01:44:12,619
[SPEAKER_02] Hvala vam na gostovanju.

4139
01:44:12,619 --> 01:44:15,140
[SPEAKER_02] Ali već prošlo sat i po?

4140
01:44:15,140 --> 01:44:16,859
[SPEAKER_02] Sat i 51.

4141
01:44:16,859 --> 01:44:18,239
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro.

4142
01:44:18,239 --> 01:44:19,060
[SPEAKER_02] Ali ajde ovako.

4143
01:44:19,060 --> 01:44:20,300
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro, brzo je prošao.

4144
01:44:20,300 --> 01:44:20,739
[SPEAKER_02] Ajde.

4145
01:44:20,739 --> 01:44:22,000
[SPEAKER_02] Ajde, još jedno pitanje.

4146
01:44:22,000 --> 01:44:25,899
[SPEAKER_02] Da li radite takve stvari

4147
01:44:25,899 --> 01:44:28,079
[SPEAKER_02] poput vizualizacije

4148
01:44:28,079 --> 01:44:31,239
[SPEAKER_02] sa svojim polaznicima

4149
01:44:31,239 --> 01:44:32,140
[SPEAKER_02] sa djecom u NTC centru?

4150
01:44:32,140 --> 01:44:32,939
[SPEAKER_01] Ima bolje koga.

4151
01:44:33,340 --> 01:44:33,560
[SPEAKER_01] Što?

4152
01:44:33,560 --> 01:44:36,359
[SPEAKER_01] Asocijacija je paralelna asocijacija,

4153
01:44:36,359 --> 01:44:37,520
[SPEAKER_01] nelogična asocijacija.

4154
01:44:37,520 --> 01:44:38,319
[SPEAKER_01] Znači mi smo jako

4155
01:44:38,319 --> 01:44:39,020
[SPEAKER_01] od toga otišli

4156
01:44:39,020 --> 01:44:40,659
[SPEAKER_01] i to je to što deca vole.

4157
01:44:40,659 --> 01:44:41,779
[SPEAKER_01] Šta bi recimo bilo

4158
01:44:41,779 --> 01:44:42,539
[SPEAKER_01] slikovno pismo

4159
01:44:42,539 --> 01:44:43,819
[SPEAKER_01] vizualizacija?

4160
01:44:43,819 --> 01:44:46,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ako nacrtam stih,

4161
01:44:46,539 --> 01:44:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] kiša pada, trava raste.

4162
01:44:48,079 --> 01:44:49,159
[SPEAKER_01] Šta ću nacrtati?

4163
01:44:49,159 --> 01:44:50,979
[SPEAKER_01] Pa kiša pada, trava raste.

4164
01:44:50,979 --> 01:44:52,699
[SPEAKER_01] A ovaj stih,

4165
01:44:52,699 --> 01:44:54,600
[SPEAKER_01] mene moja duša boli.

4166
01:44:54,600 --> 01:44:55,939
[SPEAKER_01] Šta da nacrtam?

4167
01:44:55,939 --> 01:44:57,119
[SPEAKER_01] Negdje tu više slika.

4168
01:44:57,119 --> 01:44:58,579
[SPEAKER_01] E sad mora misu dide.

4169
01:44:58,579 --> 01:45:00,020
[SPEAKER_01] Mora asocijacija.

4170
01:45:00,020 --> 01:45:01,899
[SPEAKER_01] I sad priječa moj sin Danilo

4171
01:45:01,899 --> 01:45:02,579
[SPEAKER_01] kada je bio malo

4172
01:45:02,579 --> 01:45:03,500
[SPEAKER_01] i on je hteo to da radi.

4173
01:45:03,500 --> 01:45:04,479
[SPEAKER_01] Ima je šest godina.

4174
01:45:04,479 --> 01:45:05,199
[SPEAKER_01] Šta je nacrtao?

4175
01:45:05,199 --> 01:45:07,979
[SPEAKER_01] Nacrtao je srce,

4176
01:45:07,979 --> 01:45:09,859
[SPEAKER_01] a preko srca

4177
01:45:09,859 --> 01:45:10,619
[SPEAKER_01] Hanzaplast.

4178
01:45:10,619 --> 01:45:12,560
[SPEAKER_01] To je to.

4179
01:45:12,560 --> 01:45:13,939
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam njemu

4180
01:45:13,939 --> 01:45:14,979
[SPEAKER_01] istraživo, ispitivo.

4181
01:45:14,979 --> 01:45:16,680
[SPEAKER_01] Ja tu njegu pesmicu

4182
01:45:16,680 --> 01:45:17,819
[SPEAKER_01] dan danas pokazujem

4183
01:45:17,819 --> 01:45:18,920
[SPEAKER_01] na svim seminarima

4184
01:45:18,920 --> 01:45:20,600
[SPEAKER_01] od Amerike do Australije.

4185
01:45:20,819 --> 01:45:21,500
[SPEAKER_01] da pokazujem

4186
01:45:21,500 --> 01:45:22,840
[SPEAKER_01] šta je slikovno pizmo,

4187
01:45:22,840 --> 01:45:24,439
[SPEAKER_01] a šta je asocijativno.

4188
01:45:24,439 --> 01:45:24,779
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

4189
01:45:24,779 --> 01:45:26,079
[SPEAKER_01] ima i korak dalje.

4190
01:45:26,079 --> 01:45:26,859
[SPEAKER_01] Asocijativno,

4191
01:45:26,859 --> 01:45:27,260
[SPEAKER_01] zašto?

4192
01:45:27,260 --> 01:45:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] Jer vid služi,

4193
01:45:29,119 --> 01:45:30,800
[SPEAKER_01] to je naše čulo,

4194
01:45:30,800 --> 01:45:31,600
[SPEAKER_01] naše osjetilo.

4195
01:45:31,600 --> 01:45:32,399
[SPEAKER_01] Da vidimo,

4196
01:45:32,399 --> 01:45:32,800
[SPEAKER_01] recimo,

4197
01:45:32,800 --> 01:45:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] vidimo dim.

4198
01:45:33,699 --> 01:45:35,159
[SPEAKER_01] Šta kaže mozog?

4199
01:45:35,159 --> 01:45:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] Idi gasi vatru

4200
01:45:35,920 --> 01:45:36,859
[SPEAKER_01] ili idi beži.

4201
01:45:36,859 --> 01:45:37,880
[SPEAKER_01] Koja funkcija dima?

4202
01:45:37,880 --> 01:45:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da napravi asocijaciju.

4203
01:45:39,420 --> 01:45:39,779
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

4204
01:45:39,779 --> 01:45:40,560
[SPEAKER_01] koja funkcija slike?

4205
01:45:40,560 --> 01:45:43,479
[SPEAKER_01] Pa da napravi asocijaciju.

4206
01:45:43,479 --> 01:45:44,119
[SPEAKER_01] Znači,

4207
01:45:44,119 --> 01:45:45,119
[SPEAKER_01] mi moramo da idemo

4208
01:45:45,119 --> 01:45:46,920
[SPEAKER_01] ne sa teksta na sliku,

4209
01:45:46,920 --> 01:45:48,239
[SPEAKER_01] nego moramo sa teksta

4210
01:45:48,239 --> 01:45:49,760
[SPEAKER_01] na asocijaciju.

4211
01:45:49,760 --> 01:45:51,739
[SPEAKER_01] Pa na paralelnu asocijaciju,

4212
01:45:51,739 --> 01:45:52,680
[SPEAKER_01] pa na analogičnu,

4213
01:45:52,680 --> 01:45:54,180
[SPEAKER_01] tada se mozak budi.

4214
01:45:54,180 --> 01:45:57,359
[SPEAKER_01] To je neki put za reformu

4215
01:45:57,359 --> 01:45:58,500
[SPEAKER_01] iz mog predmeta

4216
01:45:58,500 --> 01:45:59,699
[SPEAKER_01] koju je predna na fakultetu.

4217
01:45:59,699 --> 01:46:02,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nadam se da će to malo brže da ide,

4218
01:46:02,300 --> 01:46:03,439
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo za sad

4219
01:46:03,439 --> 01:46:04,859
[SPEAKER_01] bar pokušamo,

4220
01:46:04,859 --> 01:46:06,100
[SPEAKER_01] imamo početne te,

4221
01:46:06,100 --> 01:46:08,020
[SPEAKER_01] mislim imamo puno rezultata,

4222
01:46:08,020 --> 01:46:10,579
[SPEAKER_01] ali početne sad recimo

4223
01:46:10,579 --> 01:46:12,260
[SPEAKER_01] već imamo reforme Crna Gora.

4224
01:46:12,260 --> 01:46:14,939
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su odlučili da kreću na NTC.

4225
01:46:14,939 --> 01:46:16,640
[SPEAKER_01] Nema rezultata,

4226
01:46:16,640 --> 01:46:17,859
[SPEAKER_01] slabi su na PSAT-u

4227
01:46:17,859 --> 01:46:19,039
[SPEAKER_01] uz Bosnu, Albaniju,

4228
01:46:19,039 --> 01:46:20,140
[SPEAKER_01] najslabi u Evropi

4229
01:46:20,140 --> 01:46:22,239
[SPEAKER_01] i oni kreću reformu.

4230
01:46:22,239 --> 01:46:23,260
[SPEAKER_01] Već prvo za pola godina

4231
01:46:23,260 --> 01:46:24,619
[SPEAKER_01] ima jako puno rezultata.

4232
01:46:24,619 --> 01:46:26,739
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da ja se nadam

4233
01:46:26,739 --> 01:46:28,239
[SPEAKER_01] da će to malo više da se radi,

4234
01:46:28,239 --> 01:46:30,180
[SPEAKER_01] da pomognemo i deci,

4235
01:46:30,180 --> 01:46:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] a naravno i sebi.

4236
01:46:33,439 --> 01:46:35,600
[SPEAKER_00] Kapućino?

4237
01:46:35,600 --> 01:46:36,340
[SPEAKER_00] Meni isto.

4238
01:46:40,600 --> 01:46:43,020
[SPEAKER_00] Novi okus isti užitak.

4239
01:46:43,020 --> 01:46:47,720
[SPEAKER_00] Viraj okus vrhunske kvalitete.

4240
01:46:47,720 --> 01:46:49,600
